%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20argument%20over%20Christmas%20presents%20turned%20into%20a%20shooting%20that%20left%20a%20young%20mom%20dead%2C%20Florida%20police%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stock%20image%20of%20a%20crime%20scene%20tape%20crossing%20a%20road%20with%20Sheriff%20vehicles%20parked%20behind%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658bffc9ec62ab5daf7ed933%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221325%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStock%20image%20of%20a%20crime%20scene%20tape%20crossing%20a%20road%20with%20Sheriff%20vehicles%20parked%20behind%20it.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20siblings'%20spat%20over%20Christmas%20gifts%20escalated%20into%20a%20fatal%20shooting%2C%20per%20a%20Florida%20police%20statement.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%2023-year-old%20mom%20was%20carrying%20her%20baby%20when%20her%20brother%2C%2015%2C%20shot%20her%20dead%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETheir%20younger%20brother%20then%20shot%20him%20in%20return%2C%20the%20sheriff%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20argument%20over%20Christmas%20presents%20escalated%20into%20a%20fatal%20shooting%20that%20left%20a%20young%20mom%20dead%2C%20the%20Pinellas%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpcsoweb.com%2F23-163-sheriff-bob-gualtieri-holds-press-conference-to-discuss-the-arrest-of-two-juveniles-in-connection-to-a-christmas-eve-murder-%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estatement%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20on%20December%2024%20when%20three%20siblings%20were%20at%20their%20grandmother's%20home%20in%20Largo%2C%20Florida%2C%20for%20Christmas%20Eve%2C%20per%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbrielle%20Baldwin%2C%2023%2C%20Darcus%20Coley%2C%2015%2C%20and%20Damarcus%20Coley%2C%2014%2C%20had%20been%20Christmas%20shopping%20with%20their%20mother%20and%20Baldwin's%2011-month-old%20and%20six-year-old%20sons%2C%20per%20the%20detectives'%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20celebrations%20took%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worst%20when%20Damarcus%20started%20arguing%20with%20his%20older%20brother%20over%20their%20number%20of%20gifts%2C%20Bob%20Gualtieri%2C%20Pinellas%20County%20Sheriff%2C%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCPcHtIf8Ly8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epress%20conference%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDamarcus%20then%20took%20out%20a%2040-caliber%20semiautomatic%20handgun%20and%20threatened%20Darcus%2C%20Gualtieri%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDamarcus%20was%20taken%20outside%2C%20where%20Baldwin%20reminded%20her%20younger%20brother%20that%20it%20was%20Christmas%2C%20per%20the%20local%20sheriff.%20But%20Damarcus%20threatened%20to%20shoot%20both%20her%20and%20her%2011-month-old%2C%20who%20was%20in%20a%20baby%20carrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20shot%20Baldwin%20in%20the%20chest%2C%20the%20sheriff%20said%2C%20and%20seconds%20later%2C%20Darcus%20came%20out%20of%20the%20house%20brandishing%20a%2045-caliber%20handgun%20and%20shot%20Damarcus%20in%20the%20stomach%2C%20per%20the%20sheriff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDarcus%20threw%20the%20gun%20into%20a%20nearby%20yard%20and%20fled%20to%20a%20relative's%20house%2C%20where%20he%20was%20arrested%2C%20the%20sheriff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbrielle%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20nearby%20hospital%2C%20where%20she%20was%20pronounced%20dead%2C%20per%20the%20police%20statement.%20Damarcus%20underwent%20surgery%20and%20remains%20in%20stable%20condition%2C%20the%20sheriff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpon%20release%2C%20Damarcus%20will%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20Florida%20Department%20of%20Juvenile%20Justice%20to%20face%20charges%20of%20first-degree%20murder%2C%20child%20abuse%2C%20and%20being%20a%20delinquent%20in%20possession%20of%20a%20firearm%2C%20the%20sheriff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDarcus%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20mental%20health%20facility%20after%20making%20statements%20about%20harming%20himself%2C%20and%20upon%20release%20will%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20Pinellas%20Juvenile%20Assessment%20Center%2C%20the%20sheriff%20said.%20He%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20attempted%20first-degree%20murder%20and%20tampering%20with%20physical%20evidence%2C%20per%20the%20sheriff's%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20more%20than%2040%2C000%20gun-related%20deaths%20in%20the%20US%20in%202023%2C%20as%20of%20December%2027%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gunviolencearchive.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Gun%20Violence%20Archive%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnintentional%20shootings%20occur%20more%20frequently%20around%20the%20holidays%20than%20at%20any%20other%20time%20of%20the%20year%2C%20linked%20to%20increased%20time%20spent%20at%20home%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bradyunited.org%2Ffact-sheets%2Funintentional-shootings-increase-holidays%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanalysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Brady%20Center%20to%20Prevent%20Gun%20Violence%2C%20based%20on%202018-2022%20data%20from%20the%20Gun%20Violence%20Archive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%2040-caliber%20handgun%20used%20in%20the%20shooting%20was%20recovered%20from%20the%20scene%2C%20the%2045-caliber%20gun%20wasn't%2C%20the%20sheriff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20searched%20that%20area%3B%20we%20can't%20find%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Gualtieri%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20unfortunate%20reality%20is%20that%20it's%20probably%20going%20to%20be%20used%20in%20the%20next%20crime%20because%20somebody%20picked%20it%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshooting-over-christmas-presents-claims-life-young-mom-florida-police-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703680840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658bffedec62ab5daf7ed938%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshooting-over-christmas-presents-claims-life-young-mom-florida-police-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20siblings'%20spat%20over%20Christmas%20gifts%20escalated%20into%20a%20fatal%20shooting%2C%20with%20a%2023-year-old%20mom%20shot%20dead%20and%20a%20teenager%20wounded%2C%20per%20Florida%20police.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tspirlet%40insider.com%20(Thibault%20Spirlet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshooting-over-christmas-presents-claims-life-young-mom-florida-police-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Roaring%2020s%20are%20so%20back%2C%20baby!%20(Probably.%20Ok%2C%20maybe%E2%80%A6hopefully%3F)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Great%20Gatsby%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65832e4bcefc010bea25ace2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDirected%20by%20Baz%20Luhrmann.%3Cp%3EWarner%20Bros.%20Pictures%2FRoadshow%20Entertainment%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Roaring%2020s%20could%20be%20back%20as%20the%20stock%20market%20and%20economy%20show%20signs%20of%20strengthening.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20end%20of%20a%20global%20pandemic%2C%20a%20strong%20US%20consumer%2C%20and%20record%20highs%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20are%20just%20a%20few%20similarities%20between%20the%201920s%20and%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20while%20the%20Roaring%2020s%20ended%20with%20a%20stock-market%20crash%20and%20the%20Great%20Depression%20in%201929%2C%20experts%20say%20this%20time%20is%20different.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20end%20of%20a%20global%20pandemic%2C%20a%20strengthening%20US%20consumer%2C%20and%20record%20highs%20in%20the%20stock%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday's%20headlines%20sound%20a%20lot%20like%20the%20articles%20that%20were%20printed%20in%20newspapers%20across%20the%20country%20during%20the%201920s%2C%20when%20America%20was%20experiencing%20an%20economic%20boom%20driven%20by%20consumer%20spending%20and%20technological%20innovations%20following%20the%20end%20of%20World%20War%20I%20and%20the%20Spanish%20Flu%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20parallels%20are%20quite%20similar%2C%26quot%3B%20NorthEnd%20Private%20Wealth%20chief%20investment%20officer%20Alex%20McGrath%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20similarities%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-roaring-20s-return-spark-massive-rally-sp500-2023-12%5C%22%3Ehave%20sparked%20some%20speculation%20on%20Wall%20Street%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20America%20is%20again%20heading%20for%20a%20prolonged%20economic%20boom%20that%20will%20drive%20the%20stock%20market%20to%20new%20heights%2C%20akin%20to%20what%20happened%20a%20century%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ESo%2C%20are%20the%20Roaring%2020s%20actually%20back%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMarket%20veteran%20Ed%20Yardeni%20of%20Yardeni%20Research%20sure%20seems%20to%20think%20so%2C%20and%20he%20says%20it's%20likely%20to%20be%20driven%20by%20a%20surge%20in%20productivity%20that%20is%20unlocked%20by%20technological%20innovations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-roaring-20s-return-spark-massive-rally-sp500-2023-12%5C%22%3Ea%20series%20of%20research%20notes%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Yardeni%20has%20argued%20that%20adopting%20artificial%20intelligence%20could%20help%20boost%20efficiencies%20and%20profits%20at%20companies%20across%20various%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProductivity%20growth%20is%20essential%20because%20it%20can%20help%20expand%20employee%20wage%20growth%20without%20the%20negative%20byproduct%20of%20increasing%20inflation.%20That%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2024-outlook-us-economy-stock-market-jobs-inflation-interest-rates-2023-11%5C%22%3Ewould%20be%20a%20Goldilocks%20scenario%20for%20the%20economy%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20wouldn't%20be%20forced%20to%20limit%20growth%20via%20interest%20rate%20hikes%2C%20as%20they%20attempted%20to%20do%20throughout%202022%20and%20the%20first%20half%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArtificial%20intelligence%20is%20just%20one%20of%20several%20technological%20innovations%20that%20are%20likely%20to%20drive%20the%20economy%20during%20the%20Roaring%202020s%2C%26quot%3B%20Yardeni%20said%20in%20a%20note%20over%20the%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20seen%20this%20scenario%20before%2C%20where%20technology%20helps%20drive%20efficiencies%20and%20sustained%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201920s%2C%20a%20slew%20of%20technological%20innovations%20helped%20employees%20increase%20their%20efficiency%2C%20companies%20boost%20profits%2C%20and%20consumers%20save%20time.%20This%20was%20unlocked%20by%20the%20widespread%20adoption%20of%20cars%2C%20electricity%2C%20agricultural%20machinery%2C%20the%20telephone%2C%20the%20radio%2C%20and%20even%20household%20appliances%20like%20the%20refrigerator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemand%20for%20these%20new%20products%20sparked%20the%20creation%20of%20today's%20consumer%20credit%20system%2C%20with%20banks%20and%20companies%20directly%20offering%20customers%20loans%20and%20pay-as-you-go%20arrangements%20to%20boost%20product%20purchases%2C%20not%20unlike%20the%20recent%20rise%20of%20buy-now-pay-later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20advent%20of%20consumer%20credit%20further%20fueled%20the%20economic%20boom%20of%20the%201920s%2C%20which%20was%20characterized%20by%2020%25%20annual%20returns%20in%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20Infrastructure%20Capital%20Advisors%20CEO%20Jay%20Hatfield%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20expect%20that%20low%20double-digit%20stock%20market%20returns%20could%20persist%20for%20the%20next%20five%20to%20seven%20years%20until%20the%20next%20Fed%20tightening%20cycle%2C%26quot%3B%20Hatfield%20said.%20%26quot%3BSustainable%20stock%20market%20returns%20are%20primarily%20driven%20by%20earnings%20growth%2C%20not%20multiple%20expansion%2C%20so%20we%20believe%20that%20low%20teens%20returns%20are%20more%20likely%20and%20sustainable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20those%20gains%20materialize%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20would%20be%20trading%20above%2010%2C000%20by%202030%2C%20more%20than%20double%20today's%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20thinking%20lines%20up%20with%20Carson%20Group's%20global%20macro%20strategist%20Sonu%20Varghese%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-us-stocks-best-investment-next-5-years-2023-12%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20note%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20US%20stocks%20will%20be%20the%20best%20investment%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years%20with%20potential%20upside%20of%20100%25.%20A%20sustained%20rebound%20in%20productivity%20growth%20was%20the%20major%20bullish%20factor%20behind%20Varghese's%20forecast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ENot%20so%20fast%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20economy%20isn't%20out%20of%20the%20woods%20just%20yet%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-cash-better-than-stocks-2024-jpmorgan-bearish-2023-12%5C%22%3Esome%20strategists%20on%20Wall%20Street%20still%20expecting%20a%20recession%20to%20materialize%20in%202024.%3C%2Fa%3E%20And%20that%20would%20undoubtedly%20throw%20a%20wrench%20into%20the%20Roaring%2020s%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20premature%20to%20suggest%20happy%20days%20are%20here%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20Bank%20Wealth%20Management's%20chief%20equity%20strategist%20Terry%20Sandven%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BHigher-for-longer%20inflation%20and%20interest%20rates%2C%20the%20potential%20for%20corporate%20earnings%20pressures%20and%20already-evaluated%20valuations%20temper%20our%20cautiously%20optimistic%20outlook.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESandven%20said%20he%20expects%20more%20sideways%20%26quot%3Bchop%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20next%20year%2C%20reversing%20this%20year's%20trend%20of%20strong%20market%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcGrath%2C%20the%20NorthEnd%20CIO%2C%20says%20this%20year's%20trend%20of%20strong%20economic%20growth%20could%20reverse%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEconomic%20growth%20has%20certainly%20surprised%20to%20the%20upside%20in%202023%2C%20but%20that%20narrative%20may%20become%20more%20muted%20as%20the%20lingering%20effects%20of%20higher%20%5Binterest%5D%20rates%20take%20hold%20in%20our%20country%20and%20across%20the%20globe%2C%26quot%3B%20he%C2%A0said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20return%20of%20the%20Roaring%2020s%20seems%20to%20hinge%20on%20what%20Fed%20Chairman%20Jerome%20Powell%20will%20do%20with%20interest%20rates%20in%202024%2C%20combined%20with%20how%20long%20the%20consumer%20and%20jobs%20market%20can%20remain%20resilient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EThe%20spectre%20of%20the%201929%20Great%20Depression%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20chief%20investment%20strategist%20Sam%20Stovall%20of%20CFRA%20Research%2C%20the%20question%20to%20ask%20isn't%20whether%20or%20not%20the%20Roaring%2020's%20are%20back.%20He's%20instead%20wondering%20if%20an%20era%20of%20extended%20prosperity%20will%20end%20with%20the%20same%20thud%20it%20did%20a%20century%20ago%2C%20when%20the%20Great%20Depression%20struck%20in%201929%20alongside%20an%2089%25%20plunge%20in%20the%20Dow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aforementioned%20tech%20advancements%20and%20the%20consumer-credit%20system%20that%20fueled%20so%20much%20growth%20ended%20up%20being%20double-edged%20swords.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20similar%20conditions%20(consumer%20demand%2C%20economic%20expansion%2C%20technological%20innovations)%20after%20World%20War%20II.%20So%20I%20guess%20the%20real%2C%20underlying%20question%20is%20'could%20the%20US%20stock%20market%20be%20setting%20itself%20up%20for%20a%201929-like%20crash%3F'%26quot%3B%20Stovall%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20decline%20would%20mean%20complete%20and%20utter%20devastation%20for%20investors%2C%20consumers%2C%20and%20the%20global%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Stovall%20isn't%20worried%2C%20and%20stresses%20that%20this%20time%20is%20different.%20He%20says%20assorted%20checks%20and%20balances%20that%20didn't%20previously%20exist%20have%20since%20been%20put%20into%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20no%2C%20because%20financial%20market%20conditions%20today%20are%20very%20unlike%20those%20of%20the%201920s%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20we%20now%20have%20regulatory%20bodies%20and%20trading%20rules%20in%20place%20to%20avoid%20such%20outcomes%20as%20we%20endured%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20crash.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20investors%20can't%20buy%20stocks%20on%2090%25%20margin%20like%20they%20could%20during%20the%201920s%2C%20Stovall%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20while%20the%20similarities%20between%20today%20and%20100%20years%20ago%20are%20uncanny%2C%20the%20consensus%20seems%20to%20be%20that%20whatever%20age%20of%20prosperity%20awaits%20will%20stop%20short%20of%20ending%20in%20a%20cataclysmic%2C%201929-style%20disaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20true%20Roaring%2020s%20is%20upon%20us%2C%20then%20it's%20a%20great%20time%20for%20stock%20investors%20and%20economists%20to%20buckle%20in%20and%20enjoy%20the%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-economy-decade-outlook-roaring-20s-investors-crash-chances-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insid