ully%20get%20him%20the%20help%20he%20needs%2C%26quot%3B%20Cachuela%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAni-Nihoa%20told%20Hawaii%20News%20Now%20the%20couple%20had%20been%20together%20for%2011%20years%20and%20had%20been%20experiencing%20problems%20for%20some%20time.%20She%20said%20Jason%20tried%20to%20%26quot%3Bcontrol%26quot%3B%20her%20daughter%2C%20and%20that%20she%20had%20recently%20filed%20for%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20Cachuela%20had%20tried%20to%20seek%20help%20from%20authorities%2C%20but%20police%20didn't%20take%20her%20requests%20seriously%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe's%20been%20trying%20to%20tell%20the%20cops%20about%20all%20the%20issues%20that%20were%20going%20on%20about%20the%20gun%20that%20he%20pulled%20on%20her%20a%20couple%20of%20times%20already%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20threatened%20to%20kill%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20Jason%20had%20never%20been%20arrested%20despite%20police%20knowing%20he%20had%20guns%20and%20that%20he'd%20made%20threats%20against%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20system%20failed%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20now%20she's%20gone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECachuela's%20family%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hawaiitribune-herald.com%2F2023%2F12%2F24%2Fhawaii-news%2Fmother-of-3-fatally-shot-in-pearlridge-parking-garage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20Honolulu%20Star-Advertiser%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Jason%20had%20been%20tracking%20her%20with%20a%20GPS%20device%20he'd%20planted%20in%20her%20car%20and%20cellphone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20police%20are%20supposed%20to%20protect.%20They%20failed%20her%3B%20the%20law%20failed%20her%20miserably%2C%26quot%3B%20Cachuela's%20father%20Stephen%20Johnston%20told%20local%20broadcaster%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.khon2.com%2Ftop-stories%2Fshe-was-my-best-friend-father-of-woman-killed-at-pearlridge-speaks-out-about-domestic-violence%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_b