b4426c2b46286050d390cc404b3875f75c6eeec9%26postID%3D6578afbef1dbb59a62a8881d%26postSlug%3Dgrocery-shopping-costco-trader-joes-comparison-photos-2023-12%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FJoy-Costco-Treasure-Hunt%252Fdp%252F1959505009%252F%253Fasc_refurl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.insider.com%25252F%2526asc_source%253Dbrowser%2526asc_campaign%253Dcommerce-pra%2526tag%253Dbiauto-62393-20%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etheir%20first%20book%20about%20the%20wholesaler%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20to%20see%20Costco%20through%20their%20lens%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-surprising-things-i-learned-shopping-with-superfans-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20recent%20tour%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Brooklyn%20warehouse%20and%20found%20it%20to%20be%20a%20vastly%20different%20shopping%20experience%20from%20Trader%20Joe's.%20Here's%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20are%20only%20three%20Costco%20locations%20in%20and%20around%20Manhattan%2C%20making%20it%20less%20available%20to%20me%20than%20Trader%20Joe's.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223314%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Costco%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20New%20York.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6578b7ee0ec98e92f74ea7c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECostco%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20New%20York.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Noyen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccessibility%20is%20among%20the%20big%20differences%20I%20quickly%20discovered%20between%20Trader%20Joe's%20and%20Costco.%20While%20Trader%20Joe's%20has%20over%2010%20locations%20in%20the%20New%20York%20City%20area%2C%20Costco%20has%20four%20warehouses%2C%20making%20it%20way%20less%20readily%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20my%20first%20visit%20to%20Costco%20since%20I%20was%20a%20child%2C%20David%20and%20Susan%20recommended%20touring%20the%20Brooklyn%20warehouse%20because%20it's%20bigger%20and%20less%20crowded%20than%20the%20one%20in%20Harlem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20my%20apartment%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20I%20had%20the%20option%20of%20taking%20a%2025-minute%20taxi%20or%20an%20hour-long%20subway%20ride%20with%20multiple%20changes.%20Given%20I%20was%20in%20a%20hurry%20to%20meet%20the%20couple%20at%20a%20specific%20time%2C%20I%20took%20a%20taxi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20no%20plans%20to%20buy%20groceries%2C%20but%20if%20I%20had%2C%20hauling%20shopping%20bags%20back%20home%20for%20an%20hour%20would've%20been%20less%20than%20ideal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20could%20not%20have%20entered%20Costco%20without%20David%20and%20Susan%2C%20as%20a%20membership%20was%20required.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22David%20and%20Susan%20Schwartz%20outside%20of%20Costco%20in%20Brooklyn.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6578b95e7a3c8094d5dc305c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDavid%20and%20Susan%20Schwartz%20outside%20of%20Costco%20in%20Brooklyn.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Noyen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20distance%2C%20Costco%20is%20also%20currently%20more%20inaccessible%20to%20me%20than%20Trader%20Joe's%20because%20I%20am%20not%20a%20member%20nor%20do%20I%20know%20friends%20or%20family%20living%20in%20NYC%20who%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20can%20enter%20any%20Trader%20Joe's%20location%20whenever%20I%20see%20fit%2C%20I%20couldn't%20do%20the%20same%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Costco%20without%20a%20membership.%20There%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcustomerservice.costco.com%2Fapp%2Fanswers%2Fanswer_view%2Fa_id%2F857%2F~%2Fwhat-is-the-difference-between-each-type-of-membership%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree%20types%20available%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20membership%20that%20is%20most%20affordable%20and%20applicable%20to%20me%20is%20the%20Gold%20Star%2C%20which%20costs%20%2460%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20I%20was%20visiting%20with%20David%20and%20Susan%2C%20who%20are%20longtime%20members%20of%20the%20wholesaler.%20Members%2C%20they%20told%20me%2C%20can%20bring%20two%20guests%20into%20the%20store%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20couples%20or%20a%20pair%20of%20roommates%2C%20I%20can%20see%20the%20appeal%20of%20getting%20a%20membership%20and%20making%20it%20more%20affordable%20by%20splitting%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECostco%20sells%20homeware%20and%20miscellaneous%20items%2C%20while%20Trader%20Joe's%20is%20primarily%20focused%20on%20groceries.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Costco%20Brooklyn.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6578c04f50edbc52a863780e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrom%20hearing%20aids%20to%20pianos%2C%20you%20can%20buy%20more%20than%20food%20at%20Costco.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Noyen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20ancillary%20services%20like%20hearing%20tests%2C%20optical%20centers%2C%20and%20pharmacies%20to%20products%20like%20fridges%2C%20washing%20machines%2C%20pianos%2C%20and%20clothing%2C%20I%20saw%20plenty%20of%20things%20being%20sold%20at%20Costco%20that%20weren't%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20can't%20be%20said%20for%20Trader%20Joe's%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20standard%20grocery%20items%20more%20than%20anything%20else.%20However%2C%20I%20do%20most%20of%20my%20homeware%20shopping%20online%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20particularly%20see%20Costco's%20homeware%20sections%20as%20a%20massive%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBoth%20Costco%20and%20Trader%20Joe's%20offer%20%26quot%3Btreasure%20hunt%26quot%3B%20shop%20layouts%2C%20but%20I%20think%20the%20latter%20is%20easier%20to%20navigate.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Costco%20Brooklyn%20is%20bigger%20than%20any%20Trader%20Joe's%20I'd%20visited.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6578c14050edbc52a8637875%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Costco%20in%20Brooklyn%20is%20bigger%20than%20any%20Trader%20Joe's%20I'd%20visited.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Noyen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20big%20similarity%20between%20Trader%20Joe's%20and%20Costco%20is%20that%20the%20store%20layouts%20are%20constantly%20stocked%20with%20new%20and%20unexpected%20items%2C%20keeping%20shoppers%20excited%20and%20curious%20about%20what%20they'll%20see%20the%20next%20time%20they%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESusan%20described%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btreasure%20hunt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrader%20Joe's%20has%20a%20similar%20thing%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20'treasure%20hunt'%20that%20you%20don't%20know%20what%20you'll%20find%20when%20you%20go%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20navigating%20a%20treasure-hunt%20layout%20is%20much%20easier%20at%20Trader%20Joe's%20for%20one%20reason%3A%20size.%20According%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pennlive.com%2Fbusiness%2F2021%2F06%2Fget-to-know-trader-joes-13-facts-about-the-grocery-chain-coming-to-the-harrisburg-area.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20Penn%20Live%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20average%20Trader%20Joe's%20store%20is%20between%208%2C000%20and%2015%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestor.costco.com%2Fcompany-profile%2Fdefault.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECostco%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20the%20average%20size%20of%20a%20warehouse%20is%20147%2C000%20square%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20could%20also%20see%20how%20members%20can%20spend%20a%20whole%20afternoon%20wandering%20Costco%2C%20but%20I%20prefer%20shorter%20shopping%20experiences.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20tub%20of%20Maldon%20sea%20salt%20on%20sale%20at%20Costco.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656f8fef58e7c0c29a29e693%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20is%20the%20biggest%20tub%20of%20Maldon%20sea%20salt%20I've%20ever%20seen.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Noyen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20David%20and%20Susan%2C%20shopping%20at%20Costco%20in%20just%2030%20minutes%20is%20no%20easy%20task%20and%20kind%20of%20defeats%20the%20purpose%20of%20going%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20do%20that%2C%20you%20need%20to%20know%20what%20you're%20really%20looking%20for.%20You%20need%20to%20be%20disciplined%2C%26quot%3B%20David%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20problem%20is%20that%20you're%20going%20to%20miss%20really%20good%20bargains.%20You're%20going%20to%20miss%20special%20items.%20You're%20going%20to%20miss%20a%20lot%20of%20stuff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20couple%2C%20wandering%20the%20aisles%20at%20Costco%20is%20a%20perfect%20shopping%20experience.%20And%20though%20I%20get%20the%20appeal%2C%20I%20am%20much%20more%20of%20a%20get-in%2C%20get-out%20shopper.%20I%20want%20to%20get%20my%20grocery%20shopping%20done%20and%20dusted%20in%20less%20than%2020%20minutes%2C%20which%20is%20another%20reason%20why%20I%20love%20Trader%20Joe's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECostco%20has%20a%20real%20no-frills%20approach%20to%20shop%20decor%2C%20unlike%20Trader%20Joe's.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221059%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22There%20is%20no%20decoration%20in%20Costco.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6578c20150edbc52a86378f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22794%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUnlike%20Trader%20Joe's%2C%20there%20are%20no%20decorations%20in%20Costco.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Noyen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20seemingly%20zero%20attention%20directed%20toward%20decorating%20Costco%20warehouses%2C%20which%20I%20found%20a%20little%20jarring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Trader%20Joe's%20stores%20are%20often%20covered%20in%20handwritten%20signs%20and%20seasonal%20decorations%2C%20Costco's%20products%20are%20labeled%20with%20pieces%20of%20paper%20that%20look%20like%20they%20could've%20been%20made%20by%20anyone%20with%20a%20printer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20understand%20that%20Costco's%20dedication%20to%20efficiency%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20it's%20so%20successful%2C%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20decoration%2C%20I%20think%20this%20approach%20just%20makes%20the%20store%20feel%20very%20sterile%20and%20impersonal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EYou%20can%20buy%20things%20in%20bulk%20at%20Costco%20if%20you%20want%20to%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20get%20that%20choice%20at%20Trader%20Joe's.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Some%20pantry%20staples%20were%20available%20to%20buy%20in%20bulk.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656f8f240ec98e92f74c6183%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20pantry%20staples%20were%20available%20to%20buy%20in%20bulk.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Noyen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20huge%20draw%20for%20Costco%20is%20that%20members%20can%20choose%20to%20buy%20things%20in%20bulk.%20Some%20pantry%20staples%2C%20like%20rice%20and%20olive%20oil%2C%20are%20sold%20in%20huge%20portions%2C%20which%20explains%20why%20David%20and%20Susan%20say%20a%20lot%20of%20local%20restaurants%20and%20convenience%20stores%20shop%20for%20products%20at%20Costco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20also%20see%20why%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fcostco-best-things-for-moms-to-buy-for-a-big-family%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20in%20larger%20families%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20gravitate%20toward%20buying%20groceries%20at%20Costco.%20Products%20at%20Trader%20Joe's%20are%20sold%20in%20much%20smaller%20sizes%2C%20making%20it%20a%20less%20ideal%20option%20for%20bigger%20households%20or%20for%20people%20interested%20in%20stocking%20up%20on%20essentials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECostco's%20self-checkout%20and%20cashier%20combo%20at%20some%20select%20warehouses%20has%20Trader%20Joe's%20beat.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Self%20check-out%20machines%20and%20check%20out%20cashiers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656f8c0c7a3c8094d5d9e11e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESelf-checkout%20machines%20and%20checkout%20cashiers.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Noyen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBryan%20Palbaum%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Trader%20Joe's%2C%20confirmed%20on%20the%20company's%20podcast%20in%20August%20that%20there%20are%20no%20plans%20to%20add%20self-checkout%20machines%20to%20any%20store%20locations%2C%20according%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F08%2F17%2Fbusiness%2Ftrader-joe-self-checkouts-cashier%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20CNN.%3C%2Fa%3E%20In%20the%20episode%2C%20Palbaum%20described%20them%20as%20%26quot%3Bnot%20fun%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bwork.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPalbaum%20might%20not%20think%20self-checkout%20machines%20are%20%26quot%3Bfun%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20I'll%20be%20the%20first%20to%20say%20that%20waiting%20in%20a%20long%20line%20for%20a%20cashier%20at%20Trader%20Joe's%20isn't%20fun%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20available%20at%20every%20Costco%2C%20but%20there%20are%20some%20warehouses%2C%C2%A0like%20the%20one%20I%20visited%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20that%20do%20give%20customers%20the%20option%20to%20do%20self-checkout%20or%20line%20up%20for%20a%20cashier%20depending%20on%20how%20many%20items%20they're%20purchasing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCashiers%2C%20who%20do%20the%20registers%2C%20are%20really%2C%20really%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20David%20said.%20%26quot%3BMuch%20faster%20than%20a%20normal%20civilian%2C%20but%20they%20decided%20to%20keep%20this%20because%20the%20experiment%20seems%20to%20be%20working%20to%20have%20both.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20get%20why%20David%20and%20Susan%20are%20loyal%20to%20Costco%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20convinced%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0yet.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22David%20and%20Susan%20Schwartz%20are%20long-time%20fans%20of%20Costco.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657355b10ec98e92f74d9f9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDavid%20and%20Susan%20Schwartz%20are%20longtime%20fans%20of%20Costco.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Noyen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20get%20why%20David%20and%20Susan%20say%20Costco%20is%20their%20%26quot%3Bhappy%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20having%20shopped%20at%20Costco%20for%20most%20of%20their%20lives%2C%20the%20couple%20was%20in%20total%20awe%20as%20we%20made%20our%20way%20through%20the%20aisles%20and%20they%20spotted%20new%20items%20they'd%20never%20seen%20before%2C%20good%20deals%2C%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20product%20you'd%20get%20for%20the%20price.%20The%20warehouses%20are%20perfect%20for%20certain%20shoppers%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20I'm%20sticking%20to%20Trader%20Joe's%2C%20where%20I%20can%20walk%20in%2C%20enjoy%20the%20fun%20decorations%2C%20and%20walk%20out%20less%20than%20half%20an%20hour%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrocery-shopping-costco-trader-joes-comparison-photos-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703678641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6578ad8f7a3c8094d5dc273d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrocery-shopping-costco-trader-joes-comparison-photos-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Unlike%20Trader%20Joe's%2C%20Costco%20gives%20shoppers%20the%20option%20to%20use%20self-checkout%20machines%20at%20select%20locations%2C%20and%20the%20warehouses%20feature%20minimal%20decorations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mnoyen%40insider.com%20(Maria%20Noyen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrocery-shopping-costco-trader-joes-comparison-photos-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20You%20Send%20Notice%2C%20I'll%20Get%20You%20Noticed%26quot%3B%3A%20Influencer%20On%20Bournvita%20'Win'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDavid%20versus%20Goliath%20battles%20rarely%20end%20with%20a%20win%20for%20the%20little%20guy%20and%20this%20seemed%20to%20be%20the%20trajectory%20when%20an%20influencer%20took%20on%20Mondelez%20-%20which%20owns%20Cadbury%20and%20other%20huge%20brands%20-%20%C2%A0over%20the%20high%20sugar%20content%20in%20Bournvita%20in%20April.%20The%20influencer%20had%20to%20delete%20his%20video%20after%20getting%20a%20legal%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEight%20months%20on%2C%20however%2C%20the%20company%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwatch-bournvita-reduces-added-sugar-by-14-4-after-criticism-influencer-calls-it-big-win-4733774%5C%22%3Ereduced%20the%20added%20sugar%20content%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20drink%20by%2014.4%20per%20cent%20and%20the%20influencer%20is%20counting%20this%20as%20a%20major%20win%20for%20nutritional%20education%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20health%20influencer%20Revant%20Himatsingka%2C%20aka%20FoodPharmer%2C%20said%20he%20has%20also%20learnt%20many%20lessons%20along%20the%20way%2C%20and%20one%20of%20them%20is%20that%20a%20legal%20notice%20is%20just%20part%20of%20the%20process.%20Emphasising%20that%20he%20is%20not%20afraid%20of%20such%20notices%20anymore%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BIf%20you%20send%20me%20a%20legal%20notice%2C%20I%20am%20going%20to%20get%20you%20publicly%20noticed%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Pretty%20Staggering'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Himatsingka%20said%20he%20was%20working%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20came%20back%20to%20India%20this%20year.%20He%20finished%20a%20nutrition%20degree%20in%20the%20US%20and%20that's%20when%20he%20realised%20how%20important%20the%20labels%20on%20food%20packaging%20are.%20He%20said%20the%20idea%20behind%20making%20his%20videos%20is%20to%20educate%20people%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20doing%20this%2C%20so%20that%20they%20can%20make%20informed%20choices%20on%20what%20they%20are%20consuming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20big%20win.%20I%20know%2015%25%20may%20not%20sound%20like%20much%20(of%20a%20reduction)%2C%20but%20for%20a%20multinational%20corporation%20to%20do%20this%20is%20pretty%20staggering.%20I%20hope%20this%20leads%20to%20a%20chain%20reaction%2C%20and%20other%20companies%20follow%20suit%20and%20try%20to%20improve%20their%20products.%20Lakhs%20of%20parents%20are%20now%20reading%20labels%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20people%20are%20eating%20slightly%20more%20consciously%2C%20so%20it%20is%20a%20huge%20win%20overall%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMondelez%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Post%20Was%20Taken%20Down%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20influencer%20said%20he%20had%20just%20come%20back%20to%20India%20when%20he%20made%20the%20video%20on%20Bournvita.%20%26quot%3BI%20left%20my%20job%20in%20the%20US%2C%20I%20was%20making%20very%20good%20money%2C%20and%20I%20came%20back%20to%20India%20and%20made%20this%20video.%20Within%20two%20weeks%20of%20coming%20back%20to%20India%2C%20I%20got%20this%20legal%20notice.%20So%2C%20of%20course%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20family%20pressure%20because%20I%20had%20just%20left%20my%20job%20and%20was%20fighting%20against%20a%20corporate.%20So%20I%20deleted%20the%20video%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20also%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20support%20from%20the%20public.%20Someone%20put%20up%20a%20hoarding%20in%20Mumbai's%20Marine%20Drive%20on%20Bournvita's%20sugar%20content...%20It's%20been%20a%20very%20encouraging%20journey%20overall...%20They%20only%20give%2024%20hours%20to%20respond%20to%20a%20legal%20notice%20and%20I%20had%20only%20that%20much%20time%20to%20decide%20whether%20to%20take%20the%20post%20down.%20And%20I%20am%20not%20from%20a%20legal%20background%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20Afraid%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20he%20is%20still%20afraid%20of%20legal%20notices%20and%20if%20he%20has%20a%20lawyer%2C%20the%20influencer%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20a%20lawyer.%20I%20am%20not%20afraid%20of%20legal%20notices%20anymore%20because%20I%20have%20understood%20it%20is%20part%20of%20the%20process.%20If%20you%20send%20me%20a%20legal%20notice%2C%20I%20am%20going%20to%20get%20you%20publicly%20noticed.%20I%20intentionally%20sound%20aggressive%20in%20my%20videos%20because%20I%20don't%20want%20brands%20to%20scare%20me%20or%20the%20public%2C%20I%20want%20brands%20to%20be%20scared%20of%20the%20public.%20When%20I%20say%20scared%2C%20I%20mean%20accountable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Safe%20And%20Healthy%20Are%20Different'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Himatsingka%20said%20a%20lot%20of%20Indians%20are%20educated%20but%20not%20nutritionally%20literate%3B%20they%20often%20don't%20know%20how%20much%20protein%20or%20calories%20they%20need%20in%20a%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20food%20bodies%20looking%20after%20products%20sold%20in%20the%20market%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BA%20person%20should%20not%20need%20to%20be%20a%20nutritionist%20to%20find%20out%20whether%20a%20product%20is%20healthy.%20Ideally%2C%20anyone%20should%20be%20able%20to%20find%20out%20from%20the%20front%20of%20the%20package%20itself%20whether%20it%20is%20healthy%20for%20them.%20Most%20people%20blindly%20believe%20the%20marketing%2C%20that's%20why%20they%20think%20biscuits%20are%20healthy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20am%20doing%20is%20not%20rocket%20science%2C%20I%20am%20just%20reading%20a%20label%20that%20is%20already%20on%20the%20packaging.%20On%20the%20front%2C%20they%20claim%20their%20product%20helps%20increase%20bone%20strength%2C%20but%20when%20you%20turn%20the%20package%20around%20(and%20read%20the%20label)%20you%20find%20a%20large%20percentage%20of%20the%20product%20is%20sugar.%20Any%20doctor%20will%20tell%20you%20that%20sugar%20most%20likely%20reduces%20immunity%2C%20but%20on%20the%20front%20of%20the%20packet%20they%20claim%20immunity%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20influencer%20said%20there%20is%20a%20difference%20between%20what%20is%20safe%20to%20consume%20and%20healthy%20to%20consume.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20against%20junk%20food%2C%20I%20am%20against%20junk%20food%20marketing%20itself%20as%20healthy.%20A%20product%20can%20have%20nine%20bad%20qualities%20and%20one%20good%20quality%2C%20but%20it%20will%20put%20the%20one%20good%20quality%20on%20the%20front%20of%20the%20packaging...%20These%20companies%20may%20be%20legally%20correct%20but%20may%20not%20be%20ethically%20correct%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20pointed%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMatter%20of%20Choice%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMondelez%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20sugar%20in%20Bournvita%20is%20well%20below%20the%20recommended%20daily%20sugar%20limit%20for%20children.%20Asked%20whether%20it%20is%20not%20for%20parents%20to%20decide%20whether%20they%20want%20to%20give%20children%20such%20drinks%20so%20they%20actually%20have%20their%20milk%2C%20the%20influencer%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20choice%20as%20long%20as%20you%20are%20aware%20of%20what%20you%20are%20giving%20your%20child.%20In%20case%20of%20soft%20drinks%2C%20parents%20know%20it%20is%20harmful%20for%20their%20children%2C%20so%20they%20usually%20restrict%20it%20to%20once%20a%20week.%20But%20with%20drinks%20like%20Bournvita%2C%20they%20give%20it%20to%20their%20children%20twice%20a%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Himatsingka%20said%20he%20is%20not%20fighting%20against%20one%20company%20or%20many%20companies%20but%20simply%20trying%20to%20educate%20people.%20He%20said%20food%20can%20be%20made%20a%20part%20of%20the%20school%20curriculum%20and%20the%20front%20of%20the%20packaging%20can%20be%20clearer%20from%20a%20nutritional%20point%20of%20view%20-%20and%20not%20just%20filled%20with%20marketing%20messages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%205-10%25%20of%20India%20knows%20how%20to%20read%20English%2C%20but%20all%20food%20packaging%20is%20in%20English.%20Can%20there%20not%20be%20a%20QR%20code%20to%20translate%20the%20nutritional%20label%20into%20all%20other%20languages%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703678580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fi4n58lb_revant-himatsingka_625x300_24_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-you-send-legal-notice-ill-get-you-noticed-influencer-on-bournvita-win-4751679%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Eight%20months%20after%20an%20influencer%20reduced%20a%20video%2C%20Mondelez%20has%20reduced%20the%20added%20sugar%20content%20in%20Bournvita%20by%2014.4%20per%20cent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-you-send-legal-notice-ill-get-you-noticed-influencer-on-bournvita-win-4751679%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-you-send-legal-notice-ill-get-you-noticed-influencer-on-bournvita-win-4751679%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F