0to%20ground%20forces%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fac130-gunship-has-supported-special-operations-for-55-years-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3Efor%20more%20than%20five%20decades%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20AC-130J%20%26quot%3BGhostrider%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20latest%20version%20and%20was%20first%20deployed%20in%202019.%20The%20plane%20is%20revered%20among%20troops%20for%20its%20ability%20to%20linger%20over%20the%20battlefield%20and%20deliver%20heavy%20firepower%20with%20precision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Air%20Force%20is%20now%20considering%20removing%20the%20gunship's%20trademark%20weapon%20%E2%80%94%20its%20105mm%20howitzer%20%E2%80%94%20as%20soon%20as%202026%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defensenews.com%2Fair%2F2023%2F11%2F07%2Fus-air-force-may-remove-105mm-cannon-from-ac-130-gunship%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDefense%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20scenario%20where%20you're%20not%20able%20to%20just%20have%20free%20rein%20and%20fly%20over%20a%20friendly%20location%20for%20three%20hours%2C%20how%20do%20we%20beat%20our%20adversaries%20at%20that%20game%3F%26quot%3B%20an%20Air%20Force%20official%20told%20Defense%20News.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20take%20away%20our%20ability%20to%20loiter%20for%20extended%20periods%20of%20time%2C%20what's%20our%20counter-punch%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aircrew%20load%20cannon%20aboard%20AC-130%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60ec486b61b8600019f168fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221303%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20AC-130U's%20crew%20members%20load%20the%20105mm%20cannon%2C%20foreground%2C%20and%20the%2040mm%20cannon%20during%20training%20in%20September%202003.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%2FStaff%20Sgt.%20Greg%20Davis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AC-130's%20ability%20to%20