e%20air%20defensive%20systems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Air%20Force%20airman%20AC-130W%20gunship%20105mm%20artillery%20round%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658af98e1c5c7b8c9a0bffbd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20US%20airman%20hands%20a%20105%20mm%20round%20to%20a%20AC-130W%20crew%20member%20at%20Cannon%20Air%20Force%20Base%20in%20New%20Mexico%20in%20July%202020.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%2FSenior%20Airman%20Maxwell%20Daigle%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gun%20has%20been%20a%20mainstay%20of%20the%20AC-130%20for%20decades%20and%20has%20proven%20highly%20effective%20when%20used%20with%20the%20plane's%20other%20cannons%20and%20machine%20guns.%20During%20the%20Vietnam%20War%2C%20the%20AC-130%20and%20its%20predecessor%2C%20the%20AC-47%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fac130-gunship-has-supported-special-operations-for-55-years-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3Ewere%20credited%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20destroying%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20North%20Vietnamese%20and%20Viet%20Cong%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20design%20for%20the%20AC-130%20was%20to%20equip%20a%20plane%20to%20acquire%20and%20attack%20targets%20constantly%20without%20making%20multiple%20fly-bys%20like%20you%20would%20in%20a%20'fast%20mover%2C'%26quot%3B%20BA%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20jet-powered%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20making%20the%20gunship%20more%20stand-off%20rather%20than%20staying%20above%20target%20would%20completely%20defeat%20the%20purpose%20of%20its%20design%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Air%20Commando%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20gunship%20with%20aces%20up%20its%20sleeves%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AC-130J%20Ghostrider%20gunship%20green%20laser%20beam%20light%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%