unpaid-loan-by-relative-bank-responds-4751529%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fhdfc-agents-harass-mumbai-man-family-over-unpaid-loan-by-relative-bank-responds-4751529%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fhdfc-agents-harass-mumbai-man-family-over-unpaid-loan-by-relative-bank-responds-4751529%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Former%20JNU%20Employee%20Arrested%20For%20Cheating%20Professors%20Of%20Over%20Rs%2011%20Crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2063-year-old%20former%20JNU%20employee%20was%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20duping%20professors%20of%20the%20varsity%20and%20IIT%20Delhi%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%2011%20crore%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20providing%20affordable%20housing%20project%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20DDA's%20purported%20land-pooling%20policy%2C%20police%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20PD%20Gaikwad%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Gurugram%20in%20Haryana%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20FIR%20was%20registered%20on%20the%20complaints%20of%20these%20professors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20alleged%20that%20in%202015%2C%20Gaikwad%2C%20who%20was%20working%20as%20a%20scientific%20officer%20at%20the%20university's%20School%20of%20Environmental%20Sciences%2C%20formed%20the%20Noble%20Socio-Scientific%20Welfare%20Organisation%20(NSSWO)%20claiming%20to%20provide%20affordable%20housing%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20allegedly%20made%20a%20presentation%20and%20lured%20them%20to%20become%20members%20of%20the%20organisation.%20In%20his%20capacity%20as%20the%20president%20of%20the%20organisation%2C%20Gaikwad%20provided%20them%20details%20of%20a%20proposed%20housing%20project%20under%20DDA's%20purported%20land-pooling%20policy%20for%20which%20he%20said%20the%20NSSWO%20was%20in%20the%20process%20of%20procuring%20land%20in%20the%20proposed%20L-Zone%2C%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainants%20became%20members%20of%20the%20NSSWO%20and%20booked%20units%20in%20the%20proposed%20project.%20The%20complainants%20paid%20membership%20fees%20and%20payments%20for%20their%20flats%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%201%2C%202015%2C%20the%20accused%20took%20them%20to%20show%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20in%20the%20L-Zone%2C%20Najafgarh.%20However%2C%20he%20did%20not%20show%20any%20document%20supporting%20the%20purchase%20of%20the%20land.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20they%20came%20to%20realise%20that%20he%20was%20allegedly%20cheating%20them%2C%20the%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Gaikwad%20allegedly%20told%20the%20complainants%20that%20he%20was%20going%20to%20launch%20a%20different%20society%2C%20Siddhartha%20Officers%20Housing%20and%20Social%20Welfare%20Society%2C%20through%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20as%20members%20of%20the%20NSSWO%2C%20complainants%20could%20change%20their%20membership%20to%20the%20new%20society%20by%20visiting%20his%20office%20in%20JNU%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202019%2C%20the%20complainants%20were%20writing%20to%20Gaikwad%20to%20return%20their%20money.%20He%20has%20collected%20more%20than%20Rs%2011%20crore%20from%20them%20and%20misappropriated%20the%20same%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20investigation%2C%20complainants%20provided%20the%20materials%2Fbrochures%20and%20receipts%20issued%20by%20Gaikwad%20containing%20pictures%20of%20a%20housing%20project%20and%20depicting%20the%20said%20land-pooling%20policy%2C%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(EOW)%20Surendra%20Choudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaikwad%20had%20allegedly%20formed%20a%20society%20for%20cheating%20and%20became%20its%20president.%20E-mails%20sent%20by%20Gaikwad%20to%20the%20members%20on%20regular%20basis%20also%20contained%20the%20elements%20of%20inducement%20depicting%20the%20land-pooling%20policy%20of%20the%20DDA%2C%20Choudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3