t%20century%20at%20the%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKL%20has%20joined%20Pakistan's%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Azhar%20Mahmood%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F111-azhar-mahmood-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAzhar%20Mahmood%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sri%20Lanka's%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Thilan%20Samaraweera%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F367-thilan-samaraweera-playerprofile%5C%22%3EThilan%20Samaraweera%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20India's%20Virat%20Kohli%20to%20score%20at%20least%20two%20centuries%20by%20an%20Asian%20batter%20in%20SA.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sachin%20Tendulkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F14-sachin-tendulkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESachin%20Tendulkar%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20at%20the%20top%20with%20five%20hundred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20South%20Africa%2C%20KL%20has%20played%20six%20Tests%2C%20scoring%20357%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2032.45%2C%20with%20two%20tons%20and%20a%20fifty%20in%2011%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20batter%20has%20been%20great%20for%20India%20in%20testing%20SENA%20(South%20Africa%2C%20England%2C%20New%20Zealand%20and%20Australia)%20conditions%2C%20having%20smashed%20five%20of%20his%20eight%20Test%20centuries%20in%20these%20conditions.%20One%20century%20has%20come%20in%20Australia%2C%20and%20two%20have%20come%20in%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKL%20Rahul's%20special%20relationship%20with%20the%20Boxing%20Day%20Test%20continues.%20In%20his%20first-ever%20Boxing%20Day%20Test%20at%20Melbourne%20Cricket%20Ground%20(MCG)%2C%20KL%20made%20his%20Test%20debut%2C%20though%20he%20failed%20to%20make%20an%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20next%20Boxing%20Day%20Test%20at%20Centurion%20in%202021%2C%20KL%20smashed%20123%20and%2023%20to%20guide%20India%20to%20a%20113-run%20win%20over%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20in%20his%20third%20Boxing%20Day%20Test%2C%20he%20has%20smashed%20a%20century%20on%20his%20Test%20comeback%20in%20testing%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%2C%20KL%20also%20made%20a%20successful%20ODI%20comeback%20after%20battling%20injuries.%20He%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20India's%20Asia%20Cup%20triumph%20(169%20runs%20in%20three%20innings)%20and%20ran%20till%20the%20final%20of%20the%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20(452%20runs%20in%2010%20innings%20with%20a%20century%20and%20two%20fifties).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20in%20international%20cricket%2C%20KL%20has%20scored%201%2C199%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2059.95%2C%20with%20three%20centuries%20and%20seven%20fifties.%20His%20best%20score%20is%20111*.%20A%20T20I%20return%20is%20left%20for%20him%20at%20this%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20India%20was%20put%20to%20bat%20first%20by%20SA%20and%20the%20pacers%20made%20India%20struggle%2C%20reducing%20them%20to%2024%2F3.%20Then%20a%20partnership%20between%20Virat%20Kohli%20(38%20in%2064%20balls%2C%20with%20five%20fours)%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20(31%20in%2050%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20lifted%20India%20out%20of%20trouble%2C%20adding%2068%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20a%20brief%20counterattack%20by%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shardul%20Thakur%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63779-shardul-narendra-thakur-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShardul%20Thakur%3C%2Fa%3E%20(24%20in%2033%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20balls)%20and%20KL%20Rahul's%20resilient%2070*%20in%20105%20balls%2C%20with%2010%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes%20helped%20India%20to%20208%2F8%20at%20the%20day%20one%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKL%20then%20slammed%20his%20century%20on%20day%20two%20and%20took%20India%20to%20245%20all%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kagiso%20Rabada%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpl