h%2C%20in%20the%20short%20run%2C%20the%20most%20critical%20of%20these%20would%20be%20the%20return%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20office%20in%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20five%20months%20away.%20Whether%20as%20a%20propaganda%20trick%20or%20not%2C%20Modi%20has%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Findia-to-become-third-largest-economy-in-my-third-term-guarantees-pm-modi%2Farticleshow%2F106064170.cms%5C%22%3Edeclared%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20third%20straight%20win%20for%20him%20was%20a%20foregone%20conclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20political%20map%2C%20it%20is%20a%20no-brainer%20that%20an%20effective%20coming%20together%20of%20the%20significant%20sections%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20major%20states%20will%20block%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20further%20advance%2C%20and%20that%20may%20result%20in%20his%20relegation%20to%20the%20background.%20He%20appears%20to%20have%20way%20too%20many%20adversaries%20within%20the%20saffron%20universe%20who%20could%20turn%20vengeful%20if%20power%20slips%20from%20his%20grasp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20shots%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20and%20not%20a%20few%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20the%20city%20of%20the%20RSS%20headquarters%2C%20or%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Bhopal%20and%20Jaipur%2C%20to%20say%20nothing%20of%20the%20second%20or%20third%20string%20players%20in%20elsewhere%2C%20who%20now%20pretend%20to%20be%20obsequious%20or%20dutiful%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20lose%20little%20time%20in%20getting%20even%20for%20real%20or%20perceived%20slights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20A%20failure%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20parties%20to%20recognise%20the%20magnitude%20of%20the%20historical%20moment%20they%20are%20navigating%20is%20poised%20to%20leave%20each%20of%20them%20isolated.%20Unity%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20an%20existential%20imperative.%20Are%20they%20aware%20of%20this%20reality%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-morning-after-15-takeaways-from-the-four-state-election-results%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520the%2520three%2520north%2520Indian%2CBharatiya%2520Janata%2520Party%2520since%25202019.%5C%22%3Erecent%20assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20northern%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20won%20decisively%2C%20showed%20that%20the%20local%20Congress%20satraps%20were%20blissfully%20unaware%20of%20the%20great%20political%20significance%20of%20these%20particular%20elections%20and%20carried%20on%20as%20though%20it%20was%20business%20as%20usual.%20So%20was%20the%20Congress%20leadership%2C%20else%20it%20would%20have%20rapped%20the%20three%20erring%20chieftains%20on%20their%20knuckles%20for%20their%20tunnel%20vision%20when%20there%20was%20still%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20was%20candid%20enough%20to%20bring%20up%20the%20subject%20in%20the%20December%2021%20meeting%20of%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20but%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20there%20is%20no%20knowing%20that%20the%20party%20won%E2%80%99t%20fluff%20its%20lines%20again%20when%20it%20deals%20with%20partners%20and%20allies%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20parliament%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20displaced%20from%20its%20high%20perch%2030-odd%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%93%20when%20the%20party%20was%20indeed%20a%20gargantuan%20enterprise%20%E2%80%93%20it%20has%20not%20quite%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20operate%20the%20philosophy%20of%20working%20in%20tandem%20with%20entities%20some%20of%20whom%20may%20well%20have%20a%20chip%20on%20their%20shoulder%2C%20being%20state%20parties%20that%20have%20made%20space%20for%20themselves%20by%20edging%20out%20the%20Congress%20over%20time.%20Working%20in%20genuine%20partnership%20with%20the%20Congress%20is%20a%20lesson%20that%20the%20state%20parties%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20also%20need%20to%20learn%20%E2%80%93%20and%20in%20quick%20time.%20There%20is%20not%20much%20time%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComparisons%20of%20the%20present%20situation%20with%20the%20Janata%20experiment%20do%20not%20hold%20water.%20The%20entity%20that%20regional%20parties%20of%20the%20day%20(including%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20precursor%2C%20Jana%20Sangh%2C%20was%20also%20just%20that%20at%20the%20time)%20were%20called%20upon%20to%20ally%20with%20was%20not%20the%20Congress%20but%20a%20disgruntled%20Congress%20rump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20played%20a%20high-stakes%20game%20in%20the%20recent%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%20He%20would%20have%20been%20acutely%20conscious%20that%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20serious%20setback%20in%20this%20battle%2C%20the%20wolves%20within%20the%20BJP%20would%20be%20out%2C%20baying%20for%20his%20blood.%20They%20would%20question%20his%20ability%20%E2%80%93%20or%20even%20credentials%20%E2%80%93%20to%20lead%20the%20party%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20These%20polls%20were%20close%20to%20being%20a%20point%20of%20reckoning%2C%20if%20not%20a%20make%20or%20break%20moment%2C%20for%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20although%20this%20was%20not%20apparent.%20Inherent%20in%20them%20was%20the%20potential%20to%20bring%20the%2010-year%20Modi%20rule%20to%20a%20turning%20point%2C%20whether%20history%20marked%20a%20turn%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20clear%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20Congress%20opponents%20figured%20any%20of%20this.%20They%20did%20not%20discern%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20moment.%20They%20went%20about%20as%20though%20this%20was%20just%20another%20poll%20battle.%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20that%20a%20positive%20result%20would%20give%20Modi%20the%20leap%20and%20momentum%20in%20advance%20of%20the%20key%20election%20in%202024%20and%20help%20him%20set%20the%20field%20for%20the%20main%20battle%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Modi%20was%20taking%20his%20chances%2C%20he%20was%20not%20playing%20blind%20when%20he%20forced%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20key%20state%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20the%20architects%20of%20its%20past%20wins%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20%E2%80%93%20out%20of%20the%20reckoning%2C%20appealing%20to%20the%20electorate%20to%20cast%20their%20vote%20in%20his%20name.%20He%20was%20aware%20that%20the%20wind%20of%20communalism%20was%20in%20his%20sails.%20Two%20important%20considerations%20would%20have%20weighed%20as%20inordinately%20powerful%20factors%20%E2%80%93%20Ayodhya%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-leadership-shuffle-generational-change-strategy-for-modi-return%5C%22%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Leadership%20Shuffle%3A%20Generational%20Change%20or%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Strategy%20for%20a%20Return%20to%20Power%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20long%20four-year%20wait%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20decided%20to%20take%20up%20the%20Kashmir%20case%20%E2%80%93%20the%20challenge%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20jettisoning%20the%20constitutional%20autonomy%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%20The%20arguments%20being%20reported%20in%20the%20press%20gave%20ample%20indication%20which%20way%20things%20were%20going.%20To%20many%20it%20seemed%20that%20the%20timing%20of%20an%20event%20of%20such%20magnitude%20may%20not%20be%20unrelated%20to%20the%20electoral%20timetable.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffour-important-takeaways-from-the-supreme-court-ruling-on-jammu-and-kashmir%5C%22%3Ejudgment%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20on%20December%2011%2C%202023%2C%20after%20the%20recent%20assembly%20election%20results%20were%20announced%2C%20but%20forms%20a%20prelude%20to%20the%20parliament%20election%20due%20early%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArguably%20the%20most%20crucial%20event%20in%20setting%20the%20narrative%20of%20the%20new%20nationalism%20espoused%20by%20Modi%20and%20his%20party%20was%20the%20November%202019%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fayodhya-v