primary%20news%20in%20the%20Modi%20calendar%2C%20and%20is%20dutifully%20reflected%20in%20the%20mainstream%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20background%20became%20the%20setting%20for%20the%20win%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20which%20has%20unbound%20the%20Prometheus%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20who%20is%20portrayed%20as%20a%20heroic%20figure%20%E2%80%93%20greater%20than%20anything%20that%20has%20happened%20to%20the%20Hindu%20supremacist%20ideology%20since%20its%20inception.%20To%20add%20more%20grist%20to%20the%20mill%2C%20the%20temple%20disputes%20of%20Varanasi%20and%20Mathura%20appear%20to%20be%20continually%20stoked%20in%20the%20direction%20desired%20by%20the%20new%20nationalists%20by%20various%20levels%20of%20our%20judicial%20system%2C%20not%20excluding%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20BJP%20leaders%20now%20routinely%20refer%20to%20Modi%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98best%E2%80%99%20prime%20minister%20India%20has%20ever%20had%2C%20clearly%20surpassing%20Vajpayee%20and%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20great%20leaders%20of%20the%20freedom%20movement%2C%20such%20as%20Nehru%2C%20who%20is%20just%20about%20recognized%20as%20a%20former%20prime%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20and%20sought%20to%20be%20made%20less%20than%20significant.%20The%20already-established%20Modi%20cult%20owes%20not%20a%20little%20to%20its%20forceful%20promotion%20by%20Modi%20himself%2C%20who%20seeks%20to%20portray%20himself%20as%20larger%20than%20life%20and%20all-conquering.%20The%20G20%20meet%20in%20Delhi%20this%20year%20was%20an%20illustration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20the%20reign%20of%20this%20cult%20figure%20that%20a%20senior%20functionary%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple%20administration%20has%20declared%20the%20upcoming%20inaugural%20of%20the%20temple%20on%20January%2022%20as%20an%20event%20of%20history%20on%20par%20with%20the%20independence%20of%20India%20from%20British%20rule%20in%201947.%20The%20new%20chief%20minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20has%20said%20that%20the%20prime%20meridian%2C%20the%20internationally%20recognised%20zero%20degree%20longitude%20line%2C%20will%20now%20be%20made%20to%20pass%20through%20Ujjain%20in%20his%20state%2C%20which%20is%20the%20seat%20of%20the%20Lord%20Shiva%20as%20Mahakaal%20(the%20Great%20Time).%20The%20currently%20recognised%20marker%20is%20Greenwich%20near%20London%2C%20and%20the%20international%20time%20zones%20are%20calculated%20in%20relation%20to%20Greenwich%20to%20arrive%20at%20Greenwich%20Mean%20Time%20(GMT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20leader%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Hindutva%20forces%20hanker%20for%2C%20veritably%20the%20current%20%3Cem%3Eavatar%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CChakravarti%20samrat%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20ancient%20India%2C%20a%20mighty%2C%20conquering%20ruler%20who%20cannot%20be%20accountable%20to%20his%20subjects%2C%20and%20who%20is%20beyond%20questioning%20or%20reproach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20it%20is%20no%20surprise%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20declared%20to%20a%20newspaper%20in%20an%20interview%2C%20ignoring%20the%20parliament%20which%20was%20in%20session%2C%20that%20the%20December%2013%20incident%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20breach%20of%20the%20security%20system%20in%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%20and%20the%20entry%20in%20utterly%20dumbfounding%20circumstances%20of%20some%20youths%2C%20shouting%20slogans%20and%20letting%20off%20smoke-filled%20canisters%2C%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chamber%2C%20was%20%E2%80%9Cserious%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20shall%20be%20no%20debate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmodi-govts-priorities-an-mps-mimicry-not-146-suspensions%5C%22%3EModi%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20Priority%3A%20An%20MP%E2%80%99s%20Act%20of%20Mimicry%2C%20Caste%20Politics%2C%20Not%20Parliament%20Security%20Breach%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20followed%20was%20predictable%20enough%20as%20the%20presiding%20of