nsafe%20dosage.%20Now%2C%20she%20is%20seeking%20at%20least%20%2450%2C000%20in%20damages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Avrum%20Goldstein%20of%20Florida%20was%20hired%20by%20her%20legal%20team%20to%20examine%20the%20medical%20documents%20she%20received%20from%20Dr%20Molldrem%20and%20other%20physicians.%20Dr%20Goldstein%20said%20that%20Dr%20Mollgrem%20was%20correct%20in%20his%20diagnosis%20that%20%C2%A0%26quot%3Bvirtually%20every%20tooth%26quot%3B%20in%20Wilson's%20mouth%20had%20decayed.%20However%2C%20he%20also%20pointed%20out%20several%20violations%20of%20the%20duty%20of%20care.%20%26quot%3BKatie%20required%20a%20slow%2C%20thoughtful%2C%20careful%20and%20measured%20response%20to%20her%20disease.%20Trying%20to%20fill%20every%20hole%20in%20every%20tooth%20in%20her%20mouth%20in%20one%20visit%20is%20not%20only%20the%20antithesis%20of%20what%20was%20indicated%2C%20it%20is%20not%20humanely%20possible%20to%20achieve%20in%20an%20effective%20or%20constructive%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20a%20report%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Binconceivable%26quot%3B%20to%20work%20on%2028%20teeth%20in%20five%20and%20a%20half%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20neither%20Ms%20Wilson's%20susceptibility%20to%20illness%20nor%20the%20possibility%20of%20losing%20her%20teeth%20was%20addressed%20by%20Dr%20Molldrem%20in%20his%20attempt%20to%20fix%20her%20teeth%20in%20a%20single%20appointment.%20Additionally%2C%20Dr%20Molldrem%2C%20who%20has%20been%20in%20practice%20in%20Eden%20Prairie%20since%202004%2C%20was%20accused%20by%20Dr%20Goldstein%20of%20giving%20too%20much%20anaesthesia%20to%20Ms%20Wilson%20during%20the%20procedure.%20The%20doctor%20reportedly%20gave%20her%20960%20milligrams%20of%20the%20drug%2C%20over%20double%20the%20allowed%20amount%20of%20490%20milligrams%20for%20a%20long%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20the%20woman%20received%20proper%20treatment%20for%20her%20teeth%20in%20an%20%26quot%3Battempt%20to%20stabilize%20her%20mo