e%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMichael%20Schumacher%20was%20airlifted%20to%20Grenoble%20University%20Hospital%20after%20the%20accident%20where%20he%20was%20placed%20in%20induced%20coma.%20Mr%20Schumacher's%20family%20has%20remained%20extremely%20private%20since%20then%20and%20only%20provide%20fans%20with%20rare%20updates.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703670720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F9d2qa36_ralf-schumacher-michael-schumacher-afp_625x300_27_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Flife-is-unfair-michael-schumachers-brother-gives-update-on-f1-legend-4751129%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ralf%20Schumacher%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20is%20like%20it%20used%20to%20be%26quot%3B%20since%20the%20driving%20legend's%20crash.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Flife-is-unfair-michael-schumachers-brother-gives-update-on-f1-legend-4751129%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Flife-is-unfair-michael-schumachers-brother-gives-update-on-f1-legend-4751129%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Flife-is-unfair-michael-schumachers-brother-gives-update-on-f1-legend-4751129%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%20-%20Isha%20Koppikar-Timmy%20Narang%20split%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703670515000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106319046%2Cimgsize-77562.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fisha-koppikar-and-timmy-narang-part-ways%2Farticleshow%2F106319360.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106319360.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%