%20supposedly%20over%20a%20human%20trafficking%20plot%2C%20landed%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20December%2026.%20Originally%2C%20the%20Nicaragua-bound%20flight%20had%20303%20passengers.%20Only%20276%20were%20sent%20to%20Mumbai%20as%2025%20others%20requested%20asylum%20in%20France.%20Two%20passengers%20were%20detained%20for%20investigation%20but%20were%20released.%20Later%2C%20they%20were%20issued%20an%20expulsion%20order%20from%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flight%20from%20Dubai%20was%20detained%20when%20it%20stopped%20in%20France%20for%20refuelling%20at%20the%20Vatry%20airport%20east%20of%20Paris.%20The%20French%20authorities%20acted%20on%20an%20anonymous%20tip-off%20about%20alleged%20human%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20US%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20(UCBP)%20data%2C%20a%20record%20number%20of%20Indians%20-%2096%2C917%20-%20were%20arrested%20while%20crossing%20illegally%20into%20the%20US.%20This%20is%20five%20times%20more%20than%20the%202019%20figure.%20In%202019-20%2C%2019%2C883%20Indians%20were%20detained.%20In%202020-21%2C%2030%2C662%20Indians%20were%20arrested%20while%20in%202021-22%20this%20number%20was%2063%2C927%2C%20according%20to%20the%20data.%20It%20is%20interesting%20to%20note%20that%20over%2045%2C000%20Indians%20caught%20trying%20to%20enter%20the%20US%20from%20its%20southern%20border%20had%20cited%20'fear%20in%20their%20own%20country'%20as%20the%20reason.%20Indians%20are%20ready%20to%20tolerate%20indefinable%20adversities%2C%20including%20death%2C%20to%20leave%20their%20country%20and%20relocate%2C%20often%20illegally%2C%20to%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Australia%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20coincides%20with%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20latest%20film%20'Dunki'%2C%20running%20in%20theatres%20since%20its%20release%20on%20December%2021.%20At%20a%20public%20event%20to%20promote%20the%20movie%2C%20the%20superstar%20explained%20the%20unusual%20title%3A%20%26quot%3BDunki%20is%20an%20illegal%20trip%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20take%20to%20get%20out%20of%20their%20country%20across%20borders%20all%20over%20the%20world.%20It%20is%20called%20the%20Donkey%20travels%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Dunki'%20is%20a%20Punjabi%20word%20that%20means%2C%20%26quot%3Bto%20hop%20from%20place%20to%20place%26quot%3B.%20The%20film%20depicts%20the%20'donkey%20route'%20as%20an%20immigration%20technique%20to%20enter%20countries%20like%20the%20US%2C%20UK%20and%20Canada%20and%20portrays%20the%20process%20and%20problems%20along%20the%20way.%20Flights%20to%20Nicaragua%20(in%20the%20present%20case)%20or%20similar%20countries%2C%20where%20one%20can%20easily%20secure%20travel%20documents%2C%20are%20called%20'donkey'%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20of%20people%20migrating%20for%20better%20opportunities%20is%20positive.%20However%2C%20cases%20of%20cross-border%20smuggling%20of%20people%20and%20illegal%20migration%20by%20unscrupulous%20human%20smugglers%20and%20agents%20have%20also%20emerged%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20number%20of%20people%20involved%20in%20illegal%20immigration%20are%20from%20states%20like%20Gujarat%20and%20Punjab.%20Even%20on%20the%20flight%20held%20in%20France%2C%2096%20were%20from%20Gujarat.%20Both%20states%20have%20emerged%20as%20the%20hub%20of%20illegal%20migration%20to%20the%20US%20and%20Canada%20in%20recent%20years.%20Agents%20in%20these%20states%20have%20networks%20to%20smuggle%20people%20via%20different%20routes.%20Nine%20Gujaratis%20who%20left%20for%20the%20US%20through%20Ahmedabad-based%20human%20trafficking%20agents%20were%20arrested%20back%20in%20January%20but%20their%20whereabouts%20are%20not%20known%20now.%20Their%20families%20filed%20FIRs%20and%20even%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20in%20the%20Gujarat%20High%20Court.%20The%20High%20Court%20directed%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20to%20coordinate%20with%20authorities%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20islands%20to%20trace%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202022%2C%20a%20Gujarati%20family%20of%20four%20was%20found%20dead%20on%20the%20US-Canada%20border.%20The%20Patels%2C%20who%20belonged%20to%20Gujarat's%20Dingucha%20village%2C%20had%20frozen%20to%20death%20while%20attempting%20to%20illegally%20cross%20into%20the%20US%20from%20Canada.%20There%20are%20numerous%20other%20human%20tragedies%20that%20have%20unfolded%20in%20the%20recent%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20what%20drives%20the%20lust%20for%20foreign%20shores%2C%20Anshul%20Mahajan%2C%20a%20Ludhiana-based%20psychiatrist%2C%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20aspire%20to%20meet%20the%20financial%20needs%20of%20the%20family%2C%20which%20triggers%20it.%20Peer%20pressure%2C%20conversations%20in%20all%20strata%20of%20society%20around%20the%20foreign%20dream%20are%20the%20other%20factors.%20Competition%20with%20extended%20family%20or%20friends%20who%20are%20financially%20well%20off%20working%20abroad%20are%20the%20other%20factors%20contributing%20towards%20youth%20wanting%20to%20migrate%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20US%2C%20Canada%20at%20any%20cost.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20UN%20High%20Commissioner%20of%20Refugees%2C%2046%2C467%20people%20fled%20India%20and%20applied%20for%20asylum%20in%20other%20countries%20.%20Of%20this%2C%2081%20per%20cent%20applications%20were%20rejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20moot%20question%20is%20why%20so%20many%20Indians%20are%20still%20illegally%20migrating%20to%20these%20countries%2C%20undeterred%20even%20by%20death.%20The%20answer%20lies%2C%20perhaps%2C%20in%20poverty%2C%20underemployment%2C%20and%20an%20abundance%20of%20the%20poor%2C%20who%20attract%20human%20traffickers.%20Besides%20economic%20reasons%2C%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20persecution%26quot%3B%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20given%20by%20asylum%20seekers%20trying%20to%20migrate%20to%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Australia%20and%20Canada.%20Numerous%20immigration%20lawyers%20operating%20in%20these%20countries%20have%20fascinating%20narratives%20on%20the%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShalini%20Rana%2C%20a%20Delhi-based%20immigration%20consultant%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COpen%20western%20culture%2C%20the%20opportunity%20for%20casual%20relationships%2C%20drugs%2C%20a%20life%20free%20of%20parental%20watch%2C%20and%20no%20study%20pressure%20are%20the%20most%20common%20causes%20for%20migration%20among%20youth.%20A%20Canada%20visa%20facilitates%20entry%20into%20the%20US.%20People%20are%20valued%20in%20these%20western%20countries.%20Indian%20businessmen%20settled%20there%20need%20support.%20Getting%20cheap%20labour%20from%20their%20known%20circles%20back%20home%20becomes%20a%20win-win.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Rana%20adds%2C%20%26quot%3BThose%20who%20follow%20the%20illegal%20route%20sometimes%20get%20caught.%20Some%20who%20obtain%20visitors'%20visas%20get%20work%20permits%20and%20sustain%20themselves%20by%20being%20paid%20in%20cash.%20The%20cost%20of%20living%20is%20high.%20We%20are%20seeing%20a%20trend%20of%20many%20Indians%20wanting%20to%20come%20back.%20Some%20even%20say%20they%20are%20living%20abroad%20in%20'meethi%20jail'%20(sweet%20prison).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20in%20the%20police%20department%20reveal%20illegal%20immigration%20networks%20operating%20in%20Gujarat.%20Professionally-run%20agencies%20involved%20in%20human%20smuggling%20hold%20clandestine%20boot%20camps%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20Gujarat%20to%20train%20their%20clients%20and%20acclimatise%20them%20to%20tough%20terrains%20likely%20on%20their%20routes%2C%20be%20it%20in%20Mexico%20or%20Canada%2C%20as%20they%20head%20to%20the%20US.%20The%20%26quot%3Bclients%26quot%3B%20are%20taught%20to%20scale%20high%20walls%2C%20slide%20through%20barbed%20fences%2C%20deceive%20foreign%20law%20enforcement%20officials%2C%20and%20run%20long%20distances%20with%20their%20children%20and%20luggage.%20They%20are%20taught%20to%20survive%20on%20very%20little%20water%2C%20food%20and%20hostile%20weather.%20The%20training%20lasts%2015%20days%20to%20three%20months%2C%20depending%20on%20each%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20present%20incident%2C%20one%20of%20the%20alleged%20kingpins%20of%20the%20Dingucha%20case%2C%20who%20was%20allowed%20to%20go%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20police%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20evidence%2C%20may%20have%20had%20a%20role%20in%20organising%20the%20charter%20flight%20to%20Nicaragua.%20Agents%20extort%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%2060%20lakh%20and%20Rs%201%20crore%20from%20aspiring%20illegal%20immigrants%20heading%20to%20Europe%20or%20the%20US%2C%20sources%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20people%20decide%20to%20give%20up%20their%20national%20identity%20and%20passport%2C%20self-interest%20takes%20precedence.%20When%20their%20plans%20to%20reach%20their%20destination%20fail%2C%20they%20even%20concoct%20false%20narratives%20of%20persecution%20in%20India%20in%20a%20desperate%20attempt%20to%20seek%20asylum%2C%20giving%20potential%20fodder%20to%20India-baiters%20within%20the%20country%20and%20outside.%20Despite%20several%20failed%20attempts%2C%20more%20and%20more%20Indians%20are%20falling%20prey%20to%20such%20misadventures.%20Alert%20agencies%20will%20continue%20to%20foil%20these%20illegal%20trips.%20But%20what's%20needed%20is%20a%20strong%20socio-economic%20magnet%20to%20stop%20human%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703668680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fb5ee70sg_mumbai-passengers-france_625x300_27_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhen-shah-rukh-khans-dunki-unfolded-in-real-life-4750722%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Romanian%20flight%20carrying%20276%20Indians%2C%20which%20was%20grounded%20in%20France%20supposedly%20over%20a%20human%20trafficking%20plot%2C%20landed%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20December%2026.%20Originally%2C%20the%20Nicaragua-bound%20flight%20had%20303%20passengers.%20Only%20276%20were%20sent%20to%20Mumbai%20as%2025%20others%20reque%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhen-shah-rukh-khans-dunki-unfolded-in-real-life-4750722%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhen-shah-rukh-khans-dunki-unfolded-in-real-life-4750722%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhen-shah-rukh-khans-dunki-unfolded-in-real-life-4750722%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22L%26amp%3BT%20Construction%20bags%20contract%20for%20AMAALA%20project%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703668363000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2019-12%2F13%2Ffull%2F1576182364-4179.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fl-t-construction-bags-order-for-amaala-project-in-saudi-arabia-123122700420_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AMAALA%20is%20an%20ultra-luxury%20destination%20set%20in%20the%20Prince%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman%20Natural%20Reserve%20along%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20northwestern%20coast%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fl-t-construction-bags-order-for-amaala-project-in-saudi-arabia-123122700420_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fl-t-construction-bags-order-for-amaala-project-in-saudi-arabia-123122700420_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fl-t-construction-bags-order-for-amaala-project-in-saudi-arabia-123122700420_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20the%20US's%20Pannun%20Murder%20Plot%20Indictment%2C%20the%20Devil%20for%20the%20Modi%20Government%20Lies%20In%20the%20Dates%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30010249%2Findictment.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20alleged%20plot%20to%20murder%20a%20United%20States%20citizen%2C%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20on%20US%20soil%20is%20a%20much%20more%20serious%20matter%20than%20India%E2%80%99s%20government%20and%20some%20commentators%20have%20claimed.%20This%20becomes%20clear%20from%20a%20careful%20reading%20of%20the%20US%20Justice%20Department%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fd9%2F2023-11%2Fu.s._v._gupta_indictment.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecriminal%20indictment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20crucial%20details%20are%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edates%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20listed%20in%20that%20document.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20been%20accorded%20a%20state%20visit%20%E2%80%93%20the%20highest%20honour%20that%20the%20Americans%20can%20confer%20on%20a%20foreign%20leader.%20That%20brought%20him%20to%20the%20US%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodis-us-visit-subject-defence-analysis%5C%22%3Ebetween%20June%2021%20and%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20key%20day%20was%20the%2022nd.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20began%20with%20a%20meeting%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20with%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%20Modi%20then%20addressed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2FSpeeches-Statements.htm%3Fdtl%2F36714%2FAddress_by_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_to_the_Joint_Session_of_the_US_Congress%5C%22%3Ejoint%20session%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Congress%2C%20and%20that%20evening%20a%20glittering%20state%20dinner%20in%20his%20honour%20was%20held%20at%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20the%20indictment%20speaks%20of%20%E2%80%9Cengagements%E2%80%9D%20between%20%E2%80%9Chigh-level%20US%20and%20Indian%20government%20officials%E2%80%9D%2C%20this%20is%20clearly%20a%20reference%20to%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20state%20visit.%20The%20officials%20in%20India%20whom%20the%20indictment%20states%20were%20allegedly%20guiding%20the%20assassination%20plot%20through%20%E2%80%98Nick%E2%80%99%20at%20first%20urged%20that%20no%20action%20be%20taken%20during%20these%20%E2%80%9Cengagements%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20then%20for%20some%20reason%20that%20instruction%20was%20changed.%20The%20plot%E2%80%99s%20authors%20in%20Delhi%2C%20according%20to%20the%20indictment%2C%20were%20eventually%20prepared%20for%20the%20killing%20to%20take%20place%20during%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20visit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20June%2019%2C%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20%E2%80%93%20the%20alleged%20organiser%20of%20the%20murder%20%E2%80%93%20told%20the%20person%20he%20thought%20was%20a%20hit%20man%20(who%20was%20actually%20a%20US%20government%20agent%20operating%20under%20cover)%20that%20in%20light%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fterrorism-accused-hardeep-singh-nijjar-shot-to-death-in-surrey-bc-gurdwara%5C%22%3Ethe%20killing%20the%20previous%20day%20of%20a%20Sikh%20secessionist%20in%20Canada%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnow%20no%20need%20to%20wait%E2%80%9D%20to%20assassinate%20Pannun%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20June%2020t%2C%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20handlers%20in%20India%20told%20him%20that%20the%20murder%20of%20Pannun%20was%20now%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpriority%E2%80%9D.%20On%20that%20day%2C%20Gupta%20passed%20on%20the%20message%3A%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20got%20the%20go-ahead%20to%20go%20anytime%2C%20even%20today%2C%20tomorrow%2C%20as%20early%20as%20possible%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTomorrow%E2%80%9D%20was%20June%2021%2C%20the%20day%20that%20Modi%20arrived%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnikhil-gupta-pannun-assassination-plot-documents%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Nick%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20Money%20Courier%20and%20a%20Hitman%3A%20What%20New%20Documents%20Say%20About%20The%20Pannun%20Murder%20Plot%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20June%2022%2C%20the%20day%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20address%20to%20Congress%20and%20the%20state%20dinner%2C%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20contact%20in%20New%20Delhi%20told%20him%20that%20he%20had%20received%20a%20message%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9Cboss%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20that%20if%20the%20hit%20man%20could%20confim%20that%20the%20victim%20was%20at%20home%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20will%20be%20a%20go%20ahead%20from%20us%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20astonishing%20that%20this%20assassination%20could%20have%20been%20contemplated%20on%20the%20day%20that%20Modi%20addressed%20the%20US%20Congress%20and%20was%20being%20honoured%20at%20a%20state%20dinner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20indictment%20alleges%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgo%20ahead%E2%80%9D%20came%20from%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20superiors%20in%20India.%20The%20clear%20implication%20is%20that%20he%20was%20not%20a%20lone%2C%20rogue%20actor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20indictment%20speaks%20of%20a%20video%20meeting%20allegedly%20linked%20to%20the%20plot%20in%20a%20conference%20room%20in%20New%20Delhi%20with%20%E2%80%9Capproximately%20three%20other%20men%20in%20the%20room%20who%20were%20dressed%20in%20business%20attire%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20clear%20implication%20is%20that%20they%20were%20officials%2C%20possibly%20in%20an%20intelligence%20or%20security%20agency.%20They%20appear%20to%20have%20had%20their%20own%20operatives%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20messages%20to%20Gupta%20%E2%80%93%20noted%20in%20the%20indictment%20%E2%80%93%20indicate%20that%20his%20handlers%20for%20this%20operation%20had%20informants%20on%20the%20ground%20who%20were%20providing%20him%20with%20additional%20information%20on%20the%20intended%20victim.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20indictment%20also%20includes%20taped%20references%20by%20Gupta%20and%20his%20handler%2C%20CC-1%2C%20in%20which%20the%20latter%20refers%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cboss%E2%80%9D%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20title%3D%5C%22Page%2011%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20one%20point%2C%20on%20or%20about%20June%2022%2C%202023%2C%20CC-1%20messaged%20GUPTA%20that%20the%20Victim%20%E2%80%9Cis%20somewhere%20else%2C%E2%80%9D%20that%20%E2%80%9C%5Bh%5De%20is%20not%20at%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20CC-1%20%E2%80%9Cgot%20the%20message%20from%20boss.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boss%E2%80%99s%20identity%20is%20not%20revealed%20in%20the%20indictment.%20We%20do%20not%20know%20if%C2%A0%20the%20Americans%20%E2%80%93%20who%20know%20the%20identity%20of%20CC-1%2C%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20immediate%20contact%20in%20India%C2%A0%20%E2%80%93%20are%20aware%20of%20who%20the%20%E2%80%98boss%E2%80%99%20is.%20But%20the%20evidence%20in%20the%20indictment%20suggests%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cboss%E2%80%9D%20is%20likely%20to%20have%20been%20a%20senior%20official%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20security%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20the%20extremely%20over-centralised%20nature%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20it%20seems%20unlikely%20that%20this%20murder%20plot%20could%20have%20been%20planned%20without%20the%20knowledge%20of%20individuals%20very%20close%20to%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FTaHMOZe_GFw%3Fsi%3DUHrPLZpAuC2l_4LQ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20could%20create%20excruciating%20problems%20for%20the%20Indian%20authorities.%20They%20may%20need%20to%20consider%20how%20to%20treat%20a%20leading%20figure%20in%20the%20security%20services%2C%20and%20possibly%20even%20a%20senior%20political%20leader%20%E2%80%93%20with%20a%20national%20election%20looming.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20the%20supposed%20importance%20to%20New%20Delhi%20of%20US-Indian%20relations%2C%20it%20is%20remarkable%20that%20a%20murder%20of%20an%20American%20citizen%20on%20US%20soil%20could%20have%20been%20contemplated%20at%20all%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%2C%20as%20the%20indictment%20alleges%20with%20supporting%20evidence%2C%20other%20victims%20could%20also%20have%20been%20intended.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20fact%20that%20this%20attack%20on%20Pannun%20could%20have%20occurred%20during%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20state%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20borders%20on%20political%20insanity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Biden%20government%20has%20so%20far%20been%20willing%20to%20overlook%20abundant%20evidence%20supplied%20to%20it%20of%20numerous%20startling%20outrages%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20its%20allies%20within%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20include%20attacks%20on%20the%20media%20which%20persuaded%20Reporters%20Without%20Borders%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Frsf-narendra-modi-press-freedom-predators-kim-jongun-imran-khan-vladimir-putin%5C%22%3Eto%20identify%20Modi%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpredator%E2%80%9D%20of%20media%20freedom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20repressive%20actions%20against%20civil%20society%20which%20even%20targeted%20two%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%20winners%3A%20Amnesty%20International%20and%20Mother%20Teresa%E2%80%99s%20Missionaries%20of%20Charity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20apparent%20indifference%20to%20these%20issues%2C%20Indian%20leaders%20appear%2C%20astoundingly%2C%20to%20have%20believed%20that%20they%20could%20also%20get%20away%20with%20a%20murder%20of%20an%20American%20on%20US%20soil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20were%20mistaken.%20This%20is%20a%20deeply%20serious%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fjames-manor%2F%5C%22%3EJames%20Manor%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20emeritus%20professor%20of%20commonwealth%20studies%20in%20the%20School%20of%20Advanced%20Study%2C%20University%20of%20London.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703668290000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30010249%2Findictment.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fin-the-uss-pannun-murder-plot-indictment-the-devil-for-the-modi-government-lies-in-the-dates%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fact%20that%20Nikhil%20Gupta's%20alleged%20handlers%20in%20India%20told%20him%20they%20had%20the%20%E2%80%98go-ahead%E2%80%99%20to%20murder%20Pannun%20as%20early%20as%20June%2021%2C%20the%20date%20of%20Modi's%20arrival%20in%20the%20US%2C%20borders%20on%20political%20insanity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fin-the-uss-pannun-murder-plot-indictment-the-devil-for-the-modi-government-lies-in-the-dates%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAll%20Of%20A%20Sudden%20The%20Plane%20Dropped%26quot%3B%3A%2011%20Injured%20In%20Flight%20To%20Manchester%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEleven%20passengers%20onboard%20a%20charter%20flight%20were%20injured%20after%20the%20plane%20was%20caught%20in%20extreme%20turbulence%20while%20on%20its%20way%20to%20Manchester%20from%20Barbados.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EIndependent%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20Sunday%20and%20the%20pilots%20of%20the%20P%26amp%3BO%20Caribbean%20Cruise%20had%20to%20divert%20the%20flight%20with%20225%20passengers%20to%20Bermuda.%20Thirteen%20crew%20members%20on%20the%20plane%20were%20unharmed%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said.%20After%20the%20emergency%20diversion%2C%20passengers%20had%20to%20spend%20the%20Christmas%20Eve%2C%20Christmas%20Day%20and%20most%20of%20Boxing%20Day%20in%20Bermuda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20schedule%2C%20Maleth%20Aero%20Flight%201975%20had%20taken%20off%20from%20Barbados%20an%20hour%20late%20and%20was%20expected%20to%20arrive%20at%20Manchester%20shortly%20before%206am%20on%20December%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20cruising%20at%2038%2C000%20feet%2C%20the%20Airbus%20plane%20experienced%20severe%20%26quot%3Bclear-air%20turbulence%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Famericas%2Fbermuda-emergency-landing-barbados-manchester-b2469785.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndependent%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pilots%20then%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20plane%20to%20the%20nearest%20airport%2C%20Bermuda's%20LF%20Wade%20International%20Airport%2C%20touching%20down%20five%20hours%20later%20on%20Christmas%20Eve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20are%20diligently%20working%20to%20ensure%20the%20well-being%20of%20all%20involved.%20We%20are%20extremely%20grateful%20for%20the%20quick%20response%20of%20all%20our%20emergency%20services%20personnel%20who%20ensured%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20passengers%20and%20crew%2C%26quot%3B%20Bermuda's%20acting%20minister%20of%20National%20Security%2C%20Owen%20Darrell%2C%20said%20after%20the%20plane's%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20who%20was%20on%20the%20plane%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.manchestereveningnews.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fgreater-manchester-news%2Fall-sudden-plane-just-dropped-28350176%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EManchester%20Evening%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20experience%2