ng%20could%20have%20prepared%20me%20for%20this%20gripping%20tale%20of%20friendship%2C%20loss%20and%20the%20intersection%20of%20culture%20and%20politics%20served%20in%20a%20narrative%20style%20that%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20or%20experienced%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESet%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Irish%20War%20of%20Independence%2C%20the%20movie%20on%20its%20surface%20tells%20the%20story%20of%20a%20feud%20between%20two%20close%20friends%20while%20serving%20as%20a%20metaphor%20for%20the%20waning%20Irish%20nation%2C%20its%20people%2C%20their%20aspirations%20and%20the%20innate%20human%20need%20to%20be%20remembered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20funny%2C%20sad%2C%20poignant%20but%20most%20importantly%20it%20is%20very%20enjoyable%2C%20will%20keep%20you%20hooked%20through%20its%20running%20time%20and%20will%20remain%20in%20your%20thoughts%20well%20after%20its%20over!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Soumashree%20Sarkar%3A%20%3Cem%3EDecision%20to%20Leave%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Park%20Chanwook%2C%20Korean%2C%202022%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20blue%20and%20brown%20%E2%80%93%20the%20colours%20of%20the%20sky%20and%20the%20earth%20%E2%80%93%20can%20melt%20into%20each%20other%20so%20seamlessly%20and%20yet%20give%20the%20viewer%20a%20sense%20of%20menace%20is%20something%20this%20film%20teaches%20you.%20It%20marries%20a%20powerful%20plot%20to%20the%20plot%E2%80%99s%20own%20powerlessness%20when%20faced%20with%20a%20rather%20debilitating%20sort%20of%20a%20love%20story.%20You%20are%20left%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20having%20delved%20into%20a%20secret.%20Park%20Haeil%20is%20a%20noted%20actor%2C%20a%20man%20of%20many%20on-screen%20success%2C%20but%20the%20hero%20of%20the%20film%20is%20Tang%20Wei%2C%20who%20speaks%20without%20speaking%20and%20conveys%20emotions%20without%20artifice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Anirudh%20S.K.%3A%20%3Cem%3ENaduvula%20Konjam%20Pakkatha%20Kaanom%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20liked%20the%20Tamil%20comedy%20movie%20%3Cem%3ENaduvula%20Konjam%20Pakkatha%20Kaanom%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20means%20%E2%80%98Some%20pages%20from%20the%20middle%20are%20missing%E2%80%99.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20a%20guy%20who%20gets%20short-term%20memory%20loss%20before%20his%20wedding%20and%20how%20his%20friends%20help%20him%20keep%20it%20under%20wraps.%20Even%20though%20I%20struggled%20with%20the%20language%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20understand%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20wholesome%20humour%2C%20which%20was%20great.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Seema%20Chishti%3A%20Podcasts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20audio-visuals%20go%2C%20not%20films%20but%20audio%20had%20me%20hooked.%20This%20was%20the%20one%20year%2C%20other%20than%20the%20pandemic%20year%20of%202020%2C%20when%20podcasts%20spoke%20to%20me.%20The%20now%20discontinued%20scintillating%20%3Cem%3ESinica%3C%2Fem%3E%20podcast%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Rest%20is%20Politics%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EEmpire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20each%20of%20these%20would%20make%20my%20day%20each%20time%20a%20new%20episode%20popped%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Faiyaz%20Ahmad%20Wajeeh%3A%20%3Cem%3EWhile%20We%20Watched%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWatching%20%3Cem%3EWhile%20We%20Watched%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20documentary%20about%20veteran%20journalist%20Ravish%20Kumar%2C%20may%20be%20a%20tough%20and%20painful%20experience%2C%20but%20it%20gives%20a%20new%20perspective%20on%20what%20journalism%20really%20means%20in%20these%20dark%20times%20for%20Indian%20TV%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20documentary%20narrates%20the%20tale%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20deteriorating%20democratic%20framework%20and%20how%20the%20media%20has%20turned%20away%20from%20journalism%20on%20all%20the%20fundamental%20issues%20and%20important%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20explains%20how%20journalism%20is%20not%20about%20associating%20yourself%20with%20a%20sponsored%20opinion%20or%20propaganda%2C%20but%20about%20speaking%20the%20truth%20