sion%20(UGC)%20has%20issued%20a%20notification%20warning%20students%20about%20universities%20that%20are%20offering%20admission%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fdu-issues-notification-discontinue-mphil-from-next-academic-session-2736306%5C%22%3EMPhil%20(Master%20of%20Philosophy)%20programme%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20warning%20comes%20as%20many%20universities%20are%20offering%20the%20MPill%20degree%20despite%20the%20university%20body's%20cancellation%20of%20the%20course%20earlier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20had%20earlier%20announced%20that%20the%20MPhil%20degree%20course%20offered%20at%20all%20universities%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20legitimate%20and%20higher%20educational%20institutions%20were%20directed%20not%20to%20offer%20the%20MPill%20programmes.%20Further%2C%20the%20university%20authorities%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20take%20immediate%20steps%20to%20stop%20admissions%20to%20MPhil%20programme%20for%20the%202023-24%20academic%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20official%20notification%2C%20the%20university%20body%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20come%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20UGC%20that%20a%20few%20universities%20are%20inviting%20fresh%20applications%20for%20MPhil%20(Master%20of%20Philosophy)%20programme.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20it%20is%20to%20bring%20to%20the%20notice%20that%20the%20MPhil%20degree%20is%20not%20a%20recognised%20degree.%20The%20Regulation%20No%2014%20of%20the%20UGC%20(Minimum%20Standards%20and%20Procedures%20for%20Award%20of%20PhD%20Degree)%20Regulations%202022%20clearly%20states%20that%20Higher%20Educational%20Institutions%20shall%20not%20offer%20MPhil%20programme.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20regard%2C%20it%20is%20informed%20that%20the%20UGC%20has%20framed%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(Minimum%20Standards%20and%20Procedures%20for%20Award%20of%20PhD%20Degree)%20Regulations%2C2022%20which%20has%20been%20published%20in%20the%20Gazette%20of%20India%20on%207th%20November%2C%202022.%20The%20Universities%20authorities%2C%20therefore%2C%20are%20requested%20to%20take%20immediate%20steps%20to%20stop%20admissions%20to%20MPhil%20programme%20for%20the%202023-24%20academic%20year.%20Further%2C%20students%20are%20advised%20not%20to%20take%20admission%20in%20MPhil%20Programme%2C%26quot%3B%20notification%20from%20UGC%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703656980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-08%2Fegmsaeq8_students-generic_650x400_03_August_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fmphil-is-not-a-recognised-degree-university-body-warns-students-4749718%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20commission%20had%20earlier%20announced%20that%20the%20MPhil%20degree%20course%20offered%20at%20all%20universities%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20legitimate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fmphil-is-not-a-recognised-degree-university-body-warns-students-4749718%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fmphil-is-not-a-recognised-degree-university-body-warns-students-4749718%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fmphil-is-not-a-recognised-degree-university-body-warns-students-4749718%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20issues%20alert%20after%20blast%20near%20embassy%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703656886000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F14C48%2Fproduction%2F_132146058_gettyimages-1877586625-594x594.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67825697%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Authorities%20say%20nobody%20was%20injured%20in%20the%20low-intensity%20explosion%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Tuesday%20evening.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A63%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https