2ltr%5C%22%3EMohaiemen%20shows%20how%20to%20create%20space%20and%20to%20tease%20out%20the%20noise%20from%20real%20issues.%20In%20%E2%80%9CDocumentary%3A%20Social%20Realism%E2%80%99s%20Quest%20for%20Reality%E2%80%9D%2C%20for%20example%2C%20he%20offers%20a%20brief%20history%20of%20the%20development%20of%20photojournalism%20in%20recent%20decades.%20Critically%20examining%20the%20wider%20demand-elements%20in%20developing%20countries%2C%20he%20reveals%20the%20disappointing%20truth%20of%20continued%20dependence%20on%20Western%20countries%20for%20financial%20and%20technical%20aid%20as%20well%20as%20for%20recognition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFactors%20include%20a%20lack%20of%20maturity%20in%20building%20institutions%20and%20relatively%20slow%20progress%20in%20social%20acceptance%20around%20emerging%20issues%20like%20gender%20equality%20or%20same-sex%20love.%20He%20explores%20how%20images%20and%20their%20use%20in%20the%20developed%20world%20still%20fail%20to%20portray%20the%20reality%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fremembering-painter-and-poet-imroz%5C%22%3ERemembering%20the%20Magic%20of%20Painter%20and%20Poet%20Imroz%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20author%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20Bengali%20phrases%20to%20highlight%20issues%20and%20to%20offer%20remedies%20over%20a%20fairly%20long%20period%20underlines%20how%20scholars%20who%20leave%20their%20countries%20never%20stop%20yearning%20for%20their%20homeland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIs%20the%20book%20worth%20a%20reader%E2%80%99s%20time%20and%20money%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20well%20organised%2C%20with%20events%20and%20incidents%20aptly%20tagged%20to%20categories.%20It%20has%20been%20very%20carefully%20anthologised%2C%20with%20each%20piece%20stitching%20a%20narrative%20that%2C%20in%20the%20end%2C%20produces%20a%20much%20bigger%20story%20of%20the%20time.%20The%20table%20of%20contents%20alone%20would%20serve%20as%20a%20great%20archive%20of%20situations%20and%20historical%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EConflicting%20voices%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20puts%20a%20number%20of%20quality%20pieces%20in%20one%20place%2C%20some%20of%20which%20one%20may%20have%20missed%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20only%20downside%20is%20the%20printing%20quality.%20The%20current%20edition%2C%20black%20and%20white%2C%20uses%20paper%20that%20lowers%20the%20visual%20impact%20of%20some%20superbly%20curated%20photos.%20A%20niche%20market%20may%20be%20happy%20to%20absorb%20a%20slightly%20higher%20cost%20for%20better%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThose%20putting%20together%20the%20next%20edition%20might%20consider%20publishing%20the%20book%20or%20parts%20of%20it%20on%20better-quality%20paper.%20Another%20option%20would%20be%20to%20create%20a%20digital%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFinally%2C%20what%20is%20in%20this%20book%20for%20those%20familiar%20with%20Mohaiemen%E2%80%99s%20work%3F%20I%2C%20for%20one%2C%20admired%20his%20edited%20anthology%C2%A0%3Cem%3EChittagong%20Hill%20Tracts%20in%20the%20Blind%20Spot%20of%20Bangladesh%20Nationalism%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(2010)%20and%20his%20well-argued%20riposte%20to%20Sarmila%20Bose%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Cem%3EDead%20Reckoning%3A%20Memories%20of%20the%201971%20Bangladesh%20War%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(2011)%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ELike%20many%20of%20his%20art%20projects%2C%20this%20anthology%20speaks%20in%20conflicting%20voices.%20It%20promotes%20tolerance%20an