%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Haryana%20and%20Gujarat%20did%20not%20spend%20any%20of%20the%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20they%20received%20in%20total%20for%20organic%20farming%20over%20the%20last%20three%20years%20under%20the%20Paramparagat%20Krishi%20Vikas%20Yojana%20(PKVY)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2Floksabhaquestions%2Fannex%2F1714%2FAU2756.pdf%3Fsource%3Dpqals%5C%22%3EUnion%20agriculture%20minister%20Arjun%20Munda%20said%20in%20parliament%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20Haryana%20and%20Gujarat%20received%20Rs%205.05%20lakh%20and%20Rs%2010.10%20lakh%20respectively%20under%20the%20scheme%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoa%20received%20Rs%200%20and%20Telangana%20received%20Rs%2015.15%20lakh%20in%20the%20same%20time%20period%2C%20while%20other%20eligible%20states%20received%20over%20Rs%204%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttarakhand%20received%20the%20highest%20amount%2C%20at%20Rs%20180%20crore%2C%20and%20utilised%20Rs%20143%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStates%20that%20did%20not%20spend%20any%20of%20the%20funds%20they%20received%20under%20the%20scheme%20over%20the%20last%20three%20years%20are%20Karnataka%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Punjab%20and%20Telangana.%20Of%20these%2C%20Punjab%20received%20the%20highest%20amount%20at%20Rs%2018.03%20crore%2C%20the%20information%20provided%20by%20Munda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMunda%20was%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20by%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Gujarat%20Rajeshbhai%20Chudasama%20and%20BRS%20MP%20from%20Telangana%20Nama%20Nageswara%20Rao%20on%20steps%20the%20government%20was%20taking%20to%20promote%20organic%20and%20natural%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PKVY%20is%20one%20of%20two%20Union%20government%20schemes%20intended%20to%20promote%20organic%20farming%20and%20is%20implemented%20in%20all%20states%20other%20than%20those%20in%20the%20north-east%2C%20Munda%E2%80%99s%20response%20said.%20The%20other%20scheme%20exclusively%20covers%20India%E2%80%99s%20northeastern%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20involve%20direct-benefit%20transfers%20to%20farmers%20for%20using%20organic%20inputs%2C%20including%20organic%20fertilisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBoth%20the%20schemes%20stress%20on%20end-to-end%20support%20to%20farmers%20engaged%20in%20organic%20farming%2C%20i.e.%20from%20production%20to%20processing%2C%20certification%20and%20marketing%2C%20and%20post-harvest%20management%2C%E2%80%9D%20Munda%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20also%20focused%20on%20training%20and%20capacity%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20response%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20was%20promoting%20natural%20farming%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnaturalfarming.dac.gov.in%2FNaturalFarming%2FNFSystems%5C%22%3Ewhich%20differs%20from%20organic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20avoiding%20purchased%20farm%20inputs%20%E2%80%93%20under%20a%20%E2%80%98sub%20scheme%E2%80%99%20within%20the%20PKVY.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20promoted%20organic%20and%20natural%20farming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1059382%2Feco-friendly-agriculture-holds-promise-but-farmers-say-they-need-more-support-to-make-the-switch%5C%22%3Eas%20part%20of%20an%20effort%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20support%20minor%20farmers%20and%20make%20farming%20more%20climate-friendly%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20parliamentary%20response%20provided%20earlier%20this%20year%20by%20Munda%E2%80%99s%20predecessor%20as%20agriculture%20minister%2C%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2Floksabhaquestions%2Fannex%2F1711%2FAU3417.pdf%3Fsource%3Dpqals%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Haryana%20had%20been%20allocated%20Rs%2020.5%20lakh%20under%20the%20PKVY%20between%202020%20and%202022%2C%20but%20that%20it%20ultimately%20received%20Rs%205.05%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGujarat%20was%20allocated%20Rs%2041.01%20lakh%20under%20the%20scheme%20in%20that%20time%20period%20but%20received%20Rs%2010.10%20lakh.%20It%20did%20not%20spend%20this%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETomar%E2%80%99s%20response%20also%20provided%20the%20number%20of%20farmers%20across%20many%20states%20and%20Union%20territories%20who%20benefited%20from%20the%20PKVY%20between%202019%20and%202022.%20However%2C%20Gujarat%20was%20missing%20from%20this%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFunds%20could%20not%20be%20released%20to%20remaining%20states%20due%20to%20slow%20progress%20of%20the%20implementation%2Fnon-utilisation%20of%20funds%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20response%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGujarat%20did%20receive%20Rs%201.87%20crore%20under%20the%20scheme%20during%20the%20financial%20year%202023-24%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2Floksabhaquestions%2Fannex%2F1714%2FAU1489.pdf%3Fsource%3Dpqals%5C%22%3Ea%20different%20response%20by%20Munda%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20earlier%20this%20month%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703600780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04102045%2F11835209326_7c1729bdf5_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fharyana-gujarat-organic-farming-pkvy-scheme%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20states'%20low%20funding%20comes%20even%20as%20India%20has%20promoted%20organic%20and%20natural%20farming%20as%20part%20of%20an%20effort%20to%20support%20minor%20farmers%20and%20make%20farming%20more%20climate-friendly.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fharyana-gujarat-organic-farming-pkvy-scheme%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Daihatsu%20pauses%20production%20over%20safety%20scandal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703597346000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F72FA%2Fproduction%2F_132143492_daihatsulogo.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fb