es%20recovery%20rate.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-200519-1700577350.jpg%20556w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-200519-1700577350-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-200519-1700577350-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-200519-1700577350-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334640%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22291%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20surgical%20robot%20reduces%20risks%20in%20surgery%20and%20increases%20the%20recovery%20rate%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20SSI%20Innovations%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20always%20interested%20in%20minimally%20invasive%20approaches%20when%20it%20came%20to%20surgeries%20and%20not%20splitting%20open%20the%20sternum.%20This%20is%20where%20I%20got%20the%20chance%20to%20perform%20various%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F166057%2Findia-surgery-robot-innovation-gujarat-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erobotic%20surgeries%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%2030%20percent%20of%20the%20patients%20went%20home%20in%20a%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20performed%20so%20many%20robotic%20surgeries%2C%20I%20would%20come%20to%20India%20to%20train%20people%20in%20robotic%20surgeries.%20Back%20then%2C%20India%20did%20not%20have%20its%20own%20robotic%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202002%2C%20he%20performed%20his%20first%20robotic%20surgery%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CI%20kept%20coming%20back%20to%20the%20country%20but%20in%202011%2C%20I%20got%20an%20offer%20from%20a%20major%20hospital%20to%20launch%20their%20robotic%20surgery%20programme%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sudhir%20says%20he%20had%20always%20longed%20to%20be%20back%20home%2C%20so%20he%20jumped%20at%20the%20opportunity%2C%20packed%20his%20bags%2C%20and%20moved%20back%20with%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20there%20were%20only%20six%20to%20seven%20robotic%20systems%2C%20that%20too%20exported%2C%20so%20there%20were%20not%20many%20patients%20that%20could%20afford%20to%20pay%20those%20two%20to%20three%20lakh%20rupees%20more%20for%20robotic%20surgery.%20It%20was%20around%20this%20time%20when%20I%20met%20the%2022-year-old%20patient%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20incident%20made%20the%20doctor%20realise%20that%20the%20country%20needs%20a%20system%20that%20is%20cheaper.%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20of%20the%20high%20costs%20we%20cannot%20offer%20the%20best%20treatment%20to%20the%20patients%2C%20and%20to%20reduce%20the%20cost%2C%20we%20have%20to%20develop%20it%20in%20the%20country%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20doctor%20made%20a%20commitment%20to%20the%20cause%20and%20decided%20to%20put%20his%20practice%20on%20hold%20in%202013.%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20done%20over%201%2C400%20surgeries%20and%20with%20my%20knowledge%20of%20robotic%20surgeries%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20use%20my%20life%20savings%20of%204.5%20million%20dollars%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20I%20went%20to%20Germany%20to%20meet%20some%20of%20their%20scientists%20for%20an%20exchange%20of%20technology.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20not%20a%20success.%20Then%2C%20I%20came%20back%20to%20India%20and%20formed%20a%20team%20of%2010%20engineers%20and%20started%20the%20development%20out%20of%20my%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20robotic%20surgeries%20and%20how%20do%20they%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sudhir%20explains%20why%20robotic%20surgeries%20are%20important.%20%E2%80%9CDepth%2C%20precision%20and%20safety.%20Th