0in%20the%20initial%20assessment%20had%20basic%20knowledge%2C%20but%20now%20their%20learning%20levels%20have%20improved.%20Other%20than%20this%2C%20the%20dropout%20rate%20has%20reduced%20from%2050%20percent%20to%20nil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20terms%20of%20health%2C%20people%20are%20now%20able%20to%20consult%20with%20doctors%20for%20primary%20issues%20like%20common%20colds%2C%20skin%20diseases%2C%20and%20anaemia%2C%20in%20an%20easier%20and%20quicker%20way.%20Their%20health-seeking%20behaviour%20has%20also%20improved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20dedicated%20centres%20have%20been%20established%20in%20schools%20across%2025%20villages%20including%20Kalvarai%2C%20Arepalayam%2C%20and%20Hongalavadi%20benefitting%205%2C000%20students%20and%20a%20tribal%20population%20of%2012%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20success%20of%20the%20project%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20has%20announced%20plans%20to%20replicate%20the%20project%20across%20the%20state%2C%20says%20Krishnanunni.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FKathirimalai-4-1700489767.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dedicated%20centres%20have%20been%20established%20in%20schools%20across%2025%20villages%20benefitting%20tribal%20population.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FKathirimalai-4-1700489767.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FKathirimalai-4-1700489767-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FKathirimalai-4-1700489767-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FKathirimalai-4-1700489767-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebette